hadiths[409]{hadithnumber,text}:
1161,"abu-Kamil Jahdari ne kaha : hamein abdul-Wahid ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, neez abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibrahim Taimi se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kon si masjid jo zamin mein banai gaee pehli hai? aap ne farmaya : masjide-haram. maine puchha : phir kon si ? farmaya : masjid aqsaa. maine ( phir ( puchha : donon (ki tameer (ke beech kitna zamana tha? aap ne farmaya : chalis (40) baras aur jahan bhi tumharey liye Namaz ka waqt ho jaey, Namaz padh lo, wahi ( jagah ( masjid hai. abu-Kamil ki hadis mein hai : phir jahan bhi tumhari Namaz ka waqt ho jaey, usey padh lo, bila shubah wahi jagah masjid hai."
1162,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ibrahim bin Yazeed Taimi se hadis sunai, kaha : main masjid ke bahar khuli jagah ( sehan ( main apne walid ko Quran Majeed sunaya karta tha, jab main ( aayat ( sajda ki tilawat karta to wo sajda kar letey. maine unse puchha : abba jaan ! kya aap rastey hi mein sajda kar letey hain? unhon-ne jawab diya : maine Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna wo bayan kar rahe they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poori zamin par sabse pehli banai janey wali masjid ke barey mein puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : masjide-haraam. maine kaha : phir kon si ? aap ne farmaya, masjide-aqsaa. maine puchha : donon (ki tameer) ke darmyan kitna arsa tha? aap ne farmaya : chalis (40) saal , phir saari zamin ( hi ( tumharey liye masjid hai, jahan bhi tumhari Namaz ka waqt aa jaey wahin Namaz padh lo."
1163,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne bayan kya ke hamein Hushaim ne Sayyar se khabar di, unhon-ne Yazeed-al-Faqeer se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey panch cheezein ata ki gaee hain jo mujh se pahley kisi ko nahi di gain : har Nabi khas apni qaum hi ki taraf bheja jata tha aur mujhey har surkh w siyah ki taraf bheja gaya, mere liye ghaneemat ke maal halal qarar diye gaey, mujh se pahley wo kisi ke liye halal nahi kiye gaey. mere liye zamin ko paak karne wali aur sajdagaah banaya gaya, lihaza jis shakhs ke liye Namaz ka waqt ho jaey wo jahan bhi ho, wahin Namaz padh ley, aur mahina bhar ki masafat se dushmanon par taari ho janey waley raub se meri madad ki gaee aur mujhey shafaat (ka mansab ( ata kya gaya."
1164,abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne Hushaim se usi pichhli sanad se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : . . . . . phir isi tarah bayan kya.
1165,Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya ham logon ko aur logon par fazeelat milli teen baton ki wjah se hamari safein farishton ki safon ki tarah ki gain aur hamarey liye saari zamin Namaz ki jagah hai aur zamin ki khaak ham ko paak karne wali hai jab pani na miley aur aik baat aur bayan ki.
1166,"ibne-abi-Zayda ne ( abu-Malik ( Sad-bin-Tariq ( Ashjai ( se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Rabai-bin-Hirash ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, . . . . . . . . aagey pichhli hadis ki tarah hai."
1167,"Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey doosrey anbiya par chh chizon ke zariey se fazeelat di gaee hai : mujhey jaame kalimat ata kiye gaey hain, ( dushmanon par) raub w dabdabey ke zariey se meri madad ki gaee hai, mere liye ghaneemat ke maal halal kar diye gaey hain, zamin mere liye paak karne wali aur masjid qarar di gaee hai, mujhey tamam makhlooq ki taraf ( rasool bana kar) bheja gaya hai aur mere zariey se ( nabwooat ko mukammal karke ( nabwooat khatm kar di gayi hai."
1168,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey jaame kalimaat de kar bheja gaya hai aur raub ke zariey meri madad ki gaee hai, main neend ke aalim mein tha ke zamin ke khazanon ki kunjiyan mere paas la kar mere hathon mein rakh di gain. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to (apne rab ke paas ( ja chukey hain aur tum un ( khazanon) ko khod kar nikal rahe ho."
1169,"Zubaidi ne ( ibne-Shahab ( Zohri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they. . . .) Baqiya ( Yunus ki hadis ki tarah hai."
1170,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma (bin Abdur-Rehman ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah bayan kya."
1171,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu Yunus se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : dushman par raub taari karke mere madad ki gaee, mujhey jaame kalimaat se nawaza gaya aur main neend ke aalim mein tha ke zamin ke khazanon ki kunjiyan mere paas laai gain aur unhein mere hathon mein de diya gaya."
1172,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hamein bayan kin, unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein se ye ( bhi) thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : raub ke zariey meri madad ki gaee hai aur mujhey jaame kalimaat inayat kiye gaey hain."
1173,"Abdul Waris bin Saeed ne hamein abu Tayyah Zubai se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Madina ke oopri hissey mein us qabeeley mein thehrey jinhein banu-Amr-bin-Auf kaha jata tha aur wahan chaudah raatein qiyam farmaya, phir aap ne banu-Najjaar ke sardaaron ki taraf paigham bheja to wo log ( poorey ehtimaam se) talwaarein latkaey huey hazir huey. ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maano main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aap ki sawari par dekh raha hun, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke peechhey sawar hain aur banu-Najjaar ke log aap ke ird-gird hain yahan tak ke aap ne sawari ka paalaan abu Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ke aangan mein daal diya. ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ne) kaha : (is waqt tak) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jahan bhi Namaz ka waqt ho jata aap wahin Namaz ada kar letey they. aap bakriyon ke baadey mein bhi Namaz padh letey they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjid banaaney ka hukm diya gaya. ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : chunanche aap ne banu-Najjaar ke logon ki taraf paigham bheja , wo hazir ho gaey. aap ne farmaya : aey bani najaar! mujh se apne us baagh ki qeemat tay karo. unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi, Allah ki qism ! ham uski qeemat sirf Allah Taala se maangtey hain. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is jagah wahi kuchh tha jo main tumhen bata raha hun, usmein kajhooron ke kuchh darakht, mushrikon ki chand qabrein aur weeraana tha, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya, kajhoorein kaat di gain, mushrikon ki qabrein ukhedi gain aur weeraaney ko hamwaar kar diya gaya, aur logon ne kajhooron (ke tanon ( ko aik qataar mein qibley ki taraf gaad diya aur darwazey ke) taur par) donon taraf patthar laga diye gaey. ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aur log ( sahaba ( rajziya ashaar padh rahe they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke sath they, wo kehtey they : aey Allah ! be-shak aakhirat ki bhalai ke siwa koi bhalai nahi, isliye to Ansar aur muhajireen ki madad farmaa."
1174,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abu-Tayyah ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid banaaney se pahley bakriyon ke baadey mein Namaz padh liya kartey they."
1175,"(Muaz ke bajaey) Khalid, yani ibne-Haaris ne riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu Tayyah se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farma rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . . . .) aagey ( pichhli hadis ki tarah hai."
1176,"abu-Ahwas ne Abu-Ishaq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sola maah tak baitul-maqdis ki taraf (rukh karke) Namaz padhi yahan tak ke sura Baqra ki aayat : aur tum jahan kahin bhi ho apne rukh Kaba ki taraf karo, utri. ye aayat us waqt utri jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padh chukey they. logon mein se aik aadmi (ye hukm sun kar) chala to Ansar ke kuchh logon ke paas se guzra , wo (masjid bani Harisa mein, jiska naam us waqiey ke baad masjid qiblatain pad gaya) Namaz padh rahe they, us ne unhein ye ( hukm ( bataya to unhon-ne (namaz ke beech hi mein) apne chehrey Baitullah ki taraf kar liye."
1177,"Sufiyan (Sory) se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey Abu-Ishaq ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sola ya satrah maah baitul-maqdis ki taraf rukh karke Namaz padhi, phir hamara rukh Kaba ki taraf pher diya gaya."
1178,"Abdul-Azeez bin Muslim aur Malik-bin-Anas ne apni-apni sanadon se Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : log Quba mein subah ki Namaz padh rahe they, usi beech mein unke paas aaney wala aik shakhs (Ibaad-bin-Bishr (Raziallahu anhu)) aaya aur us ne kaha : bila shubah raat ( guzishta din ke aakhiri hissey mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par Quran utra aur aapko hukm diya gaya ke aap Kaba ki taraf rukh karein, lihaza tum log bhi uski taraf rukh kar lo. unke rukh Sham (Syria) ki taraf they, to (usi waqt) wo sab Kaba ki taraf ghoom gaey. Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe aur Abdullah-bin-Dinar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : log subah ki Namaz padh rahe they, unke paas aik aadmi aaya. . . . baqi hadis Imam Malik ki (pichhli ( riwayat ki tarah hai."
1179,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe aur Abdullah-bin-Dinar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : log subah ki Namaz padh rahe they, unke paas aik aadmi aaya. . . . baqi hadis Imam Malik ki (pichhli ( riwayat ki tarah hai."
1180,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh karke Namaz padha kartey they, phir ye aayat: ham aap ka chehra aasman ki taraf phirtaa hua dekh rahe hain, ham zaroor aap ka rukh us qibley ki taraf pher dengey jisey aap pasand kartey hain, lihaza aap apna chehra masjide-haram ki taraf pher lijiye. banu-Salma ka aik aadmi (Ibaad-bin-Bishr (Raziallahu anhu)) guzra, (us waqt) log (masjide-Quba mein) subah ki Namaz mein ruko kar rahe they aur aik rakaat us se pahley padh chukey they, us ne awaz di : suno! qibla tabdeel kya ja chuka hai. chunanche wo jis haalat mein they usi main ( rukoo hi ke aalim mein) qibley ki taraf phir gaey."
1181,"Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hisham ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey mere walid ( Urwa ( ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di ke Umme-Habiba aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney us girjey ka tazkira , jo unhon-ne Habsha mein dekha tha aur is mein tasweerein lagi hui thin, kaha : bila shubah wo log (pehley se aisey hi they ke) jab unmein koi nek aadmi faut ho jata to wo uski qabr par masjid bana detey aur is mein ye tasweerein bana detey. ye log qiyamat ke roz izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke nazdeek badtareen makhlooq hongey."
1182,Wakee ne kaha : hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid Urwa ke hawale se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis riwayat ki ke aap ke marzul-maut mein logon ne aap ke samney aapas mein baat cheet ki to Umme-Salma aur Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik girjey ka zikr kya. . . . . phir usi ki tarah bayan kya
1183,"( Yahya aur Wakee ke bajaey) abu-Muawiya ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : beeviyon Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik kaneesey ka zikr kya jo unhon-ne Habsha ki sarzameen mein dekha tha, usey ( kaneesa ( Mariya kaha jata tha. . . .) aagey ( un (pahley rawiyon ( ki hadis ki tarah hai."
1184,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Amr Naqid ne kaha : ham se Hashim bin-Qasim ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Sheban ne Hilal bin abi Humaid se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni us bimari mein jis se aap uth na sakey ( jaan bar na huey) farmaya : Allah Taala yahood aur nasara par laanat karey ! unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko masjidein bana liya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : isliye agar ye andesha na hota to aap ki qabr ko zahir rakha jata lekin ye dar tha ke usey masjid bana liya jaeyga (is liye Allah ki marzi se wo hujra mubaraka mein banai gaee. ( ibne-Abi-Sheba ki riwayat main ( فلولا ( ki jagah ( ولولا ( (aur agar (ke alfaz hain aur us se pahley ( qaalat ( ) unhon-ne kaha (ka lafz nahi kaha"
1185,Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah yahood ko halaak karey ! unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko sajda gaah bana liya.
1186,( Saeed ke bajaey) Yazeed bin Asamm ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah yahood aur nasara par laanat karey ! unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko masjidein bana liya.
1187,"Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah (bin Masood ( ne khabar di ke Hazrat Aaisha aur Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) donon ne kaha ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par) wafat ke lamhey ( taari huey to aap apni aik chadar apne chehrey par daltey they aur jab ji ghabrata to usey chehrey se hata letey they, aap usi haalat mein they ke aap ne farmaya : yahood aur nasara par Allah ki laanat ho ! unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko masaajid bana liya. aap un jaisa amal karne se dara rahe they."
1188,"Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aap ki wafat se panch din pahley ye kehtey huey suna : main Allah Taala ke huzoor us cheez se baraat ka izhar karta hun ke tum mein se koi mera khaleel ho kyonke Allah Taala ne mujhey apna khaleel bana liya hai, jis tarah us ne Ibrahim ko apna khaleel banaya tha, agar main apni ummat mein se kisi ko apna khaleel banata to Abu-Bakar ko khaleel banata , khabardaar ! tum se pahley log apne anbiya aur nek logon ki qabron ko sajda gaahein bana liya kartey they, khabardaar ! tum qabron ko sajda gaahein na banana, main tum ko is se rokta hun."
1189,"Haaroon-bin-Saeed eili aur Ahmed bin Esa donon ne hamein hadis bayan ki. (kaha : ( ham se ibne- Wahab ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Amr ne khabar di ke Bukair ne unse hadis bayan ki, unhein Aasim bin Umar-bin Qatada ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Ubaidullah Kholani se suna, wo bayan kar rahe they ke unhon-ne Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ko, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid ki naey sirey se tameer ke waqt logon ne unke barey mein baatein kin, ye kehtey suna : tum ne bahut baatein ki hain, halanke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna tha : jisne Allah ke liye masjid banai Bukair ne kaha : mera khayal hai, unhon-ne ye kaha is se wo Allah Taala ki raza aur khushnudi chahta hai to Allah uske liye jannat mein ghar banaega. Ahmed bin Esa ne apni riwayat main ( مثله في الجنة ( jannat mein us jaisa ( ghar ( kaha."
1190,"Hazrat Mehmood-bin Labid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne masjide-Nabawi ko naey sirey se tameer karna chaha to logon ne usey pasand na kya, unki khahish thi ke wo usey uski haalat par rehney dein, is par Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jis shakhs ne Allah ki khaatir koi masjid banai , Allah uske liye jannat mein us jaisa ( ghar ( tameer karega ."
1191,"abu-Muawiya ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim se aur unhon-ne Aswad aur Alqama se riwayat ki, un donon ne kaha : ham Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar unki khidmat mein hazir huey to wo poochhney lagey : jo ( hukmaraan aur unke sath taakheer se Namaz padhney waley unke perokar ( tum se peechhey hain, unhon-ne Namaz padh li hai? ham ne kaha : nahi. unhon-ne kaha : utho aur Namaz padho . unhon-ne hamein azan aur iqamat kehney ka hukm na diya ham unke peechhey khadey honey lagey to unhon-ne hamarey hath pakad kar aik ko apne daain aur doosrey ko apne baain taraf kar diya. jab unhon-ne rukoo kya to ham ne apne hath apne ghutnon par rakhey, unhon-ne hamarey hathon par halka sa maara aur apni donon hatheliyon ko jod kar apni donon raanon ke darmyan rakh liya. unhon-ne jab Namaz padh li to kaha : yaqinan aainda tumharey aisey hukmaran hongey jo namazon ko unke oqaat se muakhkhar karengey aur unke oqaat ko marney walon ki aakhiri jhilmilaahat ki tarah tang kar dengey. jab tum unko dekho ke unhon-ne ye (kaam shuroo) kar liya hai to tum (har) Namaz uske waqt par padh lena aur unke sath apni Namaz ko nafl bana lena aur jab tum teen aadmi ho to ikatthey khadey ho kar Namaz padho aur jab tum teen se zyada ho to tum mein se aik imam bin jaey aur jab tum mein se koi rukoo karey to apne bazu apni raanon par phaila de aur jhukey aur apni hatheliyan jod ley, (aisa lagta hai) jaisey main (ab bhi) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki (eik doosrey mein) pewasta ungliyon ko dekh raha hun aur (ungliyan pewast karke) unhein dikhaain."
1192,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir , Jarir aur Mufazzal ne mukhtalif sanadon ke sath Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se aur unhon-ne Alqama aur Aswad se riwayat ki ke wo donon Abdullah-bin-Masood ke yahan gaey. padhi. aagey abu-Muawia ki riwayat ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki, albatta ibne-Mus-hir aur ibne- Jarir ki riwayat main ( aakhiri hissey ( Is tarah hai : jaisey ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mukhalif taraf se aai hon (eik dusri mein pewast ( ungliyan dekh raha hun jabke aap rukoo ki haalat mein hain."
1193,(Aamash ke bajaey) Mansoor ne Ibrahim se aur unhon-ne Alqama aur Aswad se riwayat ki ke wo donon Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ke yahan hazir huey to unhon-ne puchha : jo tumharey peechhey hain unhon-ne Namaz padh li ? donon ne kaha : ji haan. phir wo donon ke darmyan khadey huey unmein se aik ko apni daain taraf aur doosrey ko apni baain taraf ( khada ( kya phir ham ne rukoo kya to ham ne apne hath apne ghutnon par rakhey unhon-ne hamarey hathon par) halka sa ( maara phir apne donon hath jod liye aur unko apni raanon ke darmyan rakha jab Namaz padh chukey to kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah kya.
1194,"abu-Awana ne abu Yaafoor se aur unhon-ne Musab-bin-Sad se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine apne walid ( Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) ke pahlu mein Namaz padhi aur apne donon hath apne ghutnon ke darmyan rakhey to mujhey mere walid ne kaha : apni donon hatheliyan apne ghutnon par rakho . unhon ( Musab ( ne kaha : maine dobara yahi kaam kya to unhon-ne mere hathon par maara aur kaha : hamein us se rok diya gaya tha aur hukm diya gaya tha ke ham hatheliyan ghutnon par tikaaein"
1195,abu-Ahwas aur Sufiyan ne abu Yaafoor se uper zikr ki gayi asnaad ke sath hamein rok diya gaya tak hadis bayan ki hai un donon ne iske baad wala jumla bayan nahi kya.
1196,"Wakee ne Ismail bin abi Khalid se, unhon-ne Zuber bin Adi se aur unhon-ne Musab-bin-Sad se riwayat ki, kaha : maine rukoo kya aur apne hathon ko is tarah kar liya, yani unko jodkar apni raanon ke darmyan rakh liya to mere walid ne mujh se kaha : ham isi tarah kya kartey they, phir hamein ghutnon ( par hath rakhney (ka hukm diya gaya."
1197,"Esa-bin-Yonus ne bhi isi sanad ke sath Musab bin Sad-bin-abi-Waqas se riwayat ki ke maine apne walid ke pahlu main ( khadey ho kar Namaz ( padhi, jab maine rukoo kya to apni ungliyon ko aik dusri mein daal kar donon ( hathon ( ko apne ghutnon ke darmyan rakh liya, is par unhon-ne mere hathon par maara, phir jab wo Namaz se farigh huey to kaha : ham aisey hi kya kartey they, phir hamein hukm diya gaya ke) hathon ko) utha kar ghutnon par rakhein."
1198,Hazrat Taaus bayan kartey hain ke ham ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se donon pairon par baithney ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne jawab diya : ye sunnat hai. ham ne unse kaha : hamara to khayal hai ke ye insan (ya agar raa ki zer ke sath ( رجل ( padha jaey to paon ( par zyadti hai. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ( nahi ( balke ye tumharey bani (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat hai.
1199,"ham se abu-Jafar Muhammad-bin Sabaah aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hadis bayan ki. hadis ke lafzon mein bhi donon aik doosrey ke qareeb hain. donon ne kaha : ham se Ismail bin Ibrahim ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hajjaj Sawwaf se unhon-ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne Hilal bin abi Memuna se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Muawiya bin abi Hakam Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padh raha tha ke logon mein se aik aadmi ko chheenk aai to maine kaha : ( یرحمک اللہ ( Allah tujh par raham kare. logon ne mujhey ghoornaa shuru kar diya. maine (dil mein) kaha : meri maan mujhey gum paaey , tum sab ko kya ho gaya? ke mujhey ghor rahe ho phir wo apne hath apni raanon par maarney lagey. jab maine unhein dekha ke wo mujhey chup kara rahe hain (to mujhey ajeeb laga ( lekin main khamosh raha, jab Rasulullah Namaz se farigh huey, mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan ! maine aap se pahley aur aapkey baad aap se behtar koi muallim ( sikhaney wala ( nahi dekha ! Allah ki qism ! na to aap ne mujhey daanta, na mujhey maara aur na mujhey bura bhala kaha, aap ne farmaya : ye Namaz hai is mein kisi qism ki guftgu munasib nahi hai, ye to bas tasbeeh w takbeer aur Quran ki tilawat hai. ya jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, maine kaha aey Allah ke rasool! main abhi thoda arsa pahley jahiliyat mein tha, aur Allah ne Islam se nawaaz diya hai, ham mein se kuchh log hain jo kaahinon (pesh goi karne waale) ke paas jatey hain. aap ne farmaya : tum unke paas na jaanaa. maine kaha : ham mein se kuchh log aisey hain jo badshigooni letey hain. aap ne farmaya : ye aisi baat hai jo wo apne dilon mein patey hain (eik tarah ka waham hai) ye (waham) unhein (unke ( kisi kaam se na rokey. (Muhammad) ibne-Sabaah ne riwayat ki : ye tumhen kisi sura (apne kaamon se) na rokey. maine kaha : ham mein se kuchh log lakeerein kheenchtey hain. aap ne farmaya : pichhle anbiya mein se aik Nabi lakeerein kheencha kartey they, to jiski lakeerein unke muwafiq ho jayen wo to sahi ho sakti hain. ( lekin ab iska jaanna mushkil hai.) (Muaawiya bin-Hakam (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : meri aik londi thi jo ahad aur jawaaniya ke aas-paas mein meri bakriyan charaati thi, aik din mein us taraf ja nikla to bhediyaa uski bakri ley ja chuka tha. main bhi bani-Adam mein se aik aadmi hun, mujhey bhi isi tarah afsos hota hai jis tarah unko hota hai (mujhey sabr karna chahiye tha) lekin maine usey zor se aik thappad jad diya iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aap ne meri us harkat ko mere liye badi ( ghalat ( harkat qarar diya. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya main usey aazad na kar dun? aap ne farmaya : usey mere paas ley aao. main usey lekar aap ke paas hazir hua, aap ne us se puchha : Allah kahan hai? usne kaha : aasman mein. aap ne puchha : main kon hon ? usne kaha : aap Allah ke rasool hain. to aap ne farmaya : usey aazad kar do, ye momina hai."
1200,Auzai ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki hai.
1201,"ibne- Fuzel ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne Ibrahim se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Alqama se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) Mina se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko , jab aap Namaz mein hotey they salam kaha kartey they aur aap hamarey salam ka jawab detey they jab ham Najashi ke yahan se wapas aaey, ham ne aapko (namaz mein) salam kaha to aap ne hamein jawab na diya. ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! ham Namaz mein aapko salam kaha kartey they aur aap hamein jawab diya kartey they. aap ne farmaya : Namaz main ( uski apni ( mashghooliyat hoti hai."
1202,Aamash se ( ibne- Fuzel ke bajaey) Hareem bin Sufiyan ne uper zikr ki gaee sanad ke sath usi ke misl hadis bayan ki.
1203,"Hushaim ne Ismail bin abi Khalid se, unhon-ne Haris bin shabeel se, unhon-ne abu-Umar w Shebani se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Namaz mein baat cheet kar liya kartey they, aik aadmi Namaz main apne sathi se guftgu kar leta tha yahan tak ke ye aayat utri, (  وقوم للہ قنتین) Allah ke huzoor intihai khushoo w khuzu ke aalim mein khatrey ho to hamein khamosh rehney ka hukm diya gaya hamein guftgu karne se rok diya gaya."
1204,"(Hushaim ke bajaey) Abdullah-bin-Numair, Wakee aur Esa-bin-Yonus ne Ismail bin abi Khalid se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki."
1205,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne apni apni sanad ke sath Leis (bin Sad ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey kisi zarurat ke liye bheja , phir main aapko aa kar mila, aap safar mein they Quteba ne kaha : aap Namaz padh rahe they. maine aapko salam kaha, aap ne mujhey ishara farmaya, jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to mujhey bulwaya aur farmaya : abhi tum ne salam kaha jabke mein Namaz padh raha tha aur us waqt ( sawari par Namaz padhtey huey) aap ka rukh mashriq ki taraf tha."
1206,"Zuhair ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey kaam ke liye bheja aur aap banu-Mustaliq ki taraf ja rahe they, main wapsi par aap ke paas aaya to aap oont par Namaz padh rahe they, maine aap se baat ki to aap ne mujhey hath se is tarah ishara kya. Zuhair ne apne hath se ishara karke dikhaya . maine dobara baat ki to mujhey is tarah (ishaarey se kuchh) kaha, Zuhair ne bhi apne hath se zamin ki taraf ishara kya aur main sun raha tha ke aap qirat farma rahe hain, aap ( rukoo w sujood ke liye) sar se ishara farmatey they, jab aap farigh huey to puchha jis kaam ke liye maine bheja tha tum ne (iske barey mein) kya kya? mujhey tum se guftgu karne se iske siwa kisi cheez ne nahi rokaa ke main Namaz padh raha tha. Zuhair ne kaha : abu-Zubair Kaba ki taraf rukh karke baithey huey they, abu-Zubair ne Banu-Mustaliq ki taraf ishara kya aur unhon ( abu-Zubair ( ne hath se qibley ki dusri samt ki taraf ishara kya ( sawari par Namaz ke doran mein aap ka rukh Kaba ki taraf nahi tha. ("
1207,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Kasir (bin shanzeer ( se, unhon-ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar mein they, aap ne mujhey kisi kaam se bheja , main wapas aaya to aap apni sawari par Namaz padh rahe they aur aap ka rukh qibley ki bajaey dusri taraf tha, maine aapko salam kaha to aap ne mujhey salam ka jawab na diya, jab aap ne salam pher liya to farmaya : tumharey salam ka jawab deney se mujhey sirf is baat ne roka ke main Namaz padh raha tha."
1208,"Abdul-Waris bin Saeed ne kaha : hamein Kasir bin shanzeer ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey kisi kaam ki gharaz se bhejaa. . . . . . . . . aagey Hammad-bin-Zaid ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
1209,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur Ishaq-bin-Mansur ne kaha : hamein Nazar-bin-Shumail ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Muhammad ne, jo ibne- Ziyad hai, hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha, maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : guzishta raat aik sarkash jin mujh par hamley karne laga taake meri Namaz tod de. Allah Taala ne usey mere qaabu mein kar diya to maine zor se uska gila ghonta aur ye irada kya ke usey masjid ke sutunon mein se kisi sutoon ke sath baandh dun taake subah ko tum sab dekh sako, phir mujhey apne bhai Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ka ye qaul yad aa gaya : aey mere rab! mujhey bakhsh de aur mujhey aisi hukumat de jo mere baad kisi ke laaiq na ho (to maine usey chhod diyaa) aur Allah ne us (jin ( ko ruswa karke lota diya. ibne- Mansoor ne kaha : Shoba ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se riwayat ki."
1210,"Muhammad-bin Bishr ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis sunai aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Shababa ne hadis sunai, un donon ( ibne- Jafar aur Shababaa ( ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis riwayat ki. ibne- Jafar ki riwayat mein maine iska gila ghonta ke alfaz nahi jabke ibne-abi-Shabeeh ne apni riwayat mein kaha : maine usey peechhey dhakka diya."
1211,"Hazrat abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qiyam (ki haalat ( mein they ke ham ne aapko ye kehtey huey suna : main tujh se Allah ki panah mein aata hun. phir aap ne farmaya : main tujh par Allah ki laanat bhejta hun. aap ne ye teen baar kaha aur aap ne apna hath badhaya , maano ke aap kisi cheez ko pakad rahe hain, jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to ham ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! ham ne aapko Namaz mein kuchh kehtey suna hai jo us se pahley aapko kabhi kehtey nahi suna aur ham ne aapko dekha ke aap ne apna hath ( aagey ( badhaya . aap ne farmaya Allah ka dushman iblees aag ka aik shola lekar aaya tha taake usey mere chehrey par daal de, maine teen baar ""main tujh se Allah ki panaah mangta hun"" kaha, phir maine teen baar kaha : ""main tujh par Allah ki kaamil laanat bhejta hun."" wo phir bhi peechhey na hata to maine usey pakadne ka irada kar liya. Allah ki qism ! agar hamarey bhai Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ki dua na hoti to wo subah tak bandha rehta aur Madina walon ke bachchey uske sath kheltey ."
1212,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima bin Qanab aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne kaha : hamein Imam Malik ne hadis sunai. dusri sanad mein Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik se kaha : kya aapko Aamir bin-Abdullah-bin Zuber ne Amr bin Sulaim Zarqi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey ye hadis sunai thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sahibzadi Zenab aur abu al-Aas bin Rabe (Raziallahu anhu) taala anhumaa ki beti Amama (Raziallahu anhu) ko utha kar Namaz padh letey they, jab aap khadey hotey to usey utha letey aur jab sajda kartey to usey (zameen par) bitha detey they? Yahya ne kaha : Imam Malik ne jawab diya : haan (ye riwayat mujhey sunai thi.)"
1213,"Usman bin abi Sulaiman aur ibne-Ajlan donon ne Aamir bin-Abdullah-bin Zuber ko Amr bin-Sulaim Zarqi se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Qatada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha. aap logon ki imamat kar rahe they, aur abu al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti Amama (Raziallahu anha) jo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ki beti thin, aap ke kandhey par thin, jab aap rukoo mein jatey to unhein kandhey se utaar detey aur jab sajdey se uthtey to phir se unhein utha letey."
1214,"( Bukair ( bin-Abdullah ( ne Amr bin Sulaim Zarqi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat abu Qatada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap logon ko Namaz padha rahe they aur abu al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti Amama (Raziallahu anha) aap ki gardan par thin, jab aap sajda kartey to unhein utaar detey."
1215,"Saeed Maqbari ne Amr bin Sulaim Zarqi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : ham masjid mein baithey huey they ke usi beech main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( ghar se) nikal kar hamarey paas tashrif laey. . . . . .) aagey ( uper zikr ki gaee rawiyon ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar unhon ( Saeed Maqbari ( ne ye bayan nahi kya ke us Namaz mein aap ne logon ki imamat farmai thi."
1216,"Abdul-Azeez bin abi Hazim ne apne walid se khabar di ke kuchh log Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unhon-ne member nabwi ke barey mein main bahas ki thi ke wo kis lakdi se bana hai? unhon ( Sehal (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : haan ! Allah ki qism ! main achi tarah janta hun ke wo kis lakdi ka hai aur usey kis ne banaya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab pahley din is par baithey they, maine aapko dekha tha. main ( abu-Hazim ( ne kaha : abu Abbas ! phir to (aap ( hamein ( uski ( tafseel bataiye . unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aurat ki taraf paigham bhejaa. abu-Hazim ne kaha : wo us din uska naam bhi bata rahe they aur kaha, apne badhai ghulam ko dekho (aur kaho ( wo mere liye lakdiyan ( jodkar member ( bana de taake main is par se logon se guftgu kya karun. to usne ye teen seedhiyan banaain, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske barey mein hukm diya aur usey us jagah rakh diya gaya aur ye Madina ke jangal ke darakht jhaau (ki lakdi) se bana tha. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap is par khadey huey aur takbeer kahi , logon ne bhi aap ke peechhey takbeer kahi jabke aap member hi par they, phir aap (ne rukoo se sar uthaya) uthey aur ultey paon nichey utrey aur member ki jad main (jahan wo rakha hua tha) sajda kya, phir dobara wahi kya ( member par khadey ho gaey ( yahan tak ke Namaz poori karke farigh huey, phir logon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya : logo ! maine ye kaam isliye kya hai taake tum (mujhey dekhtey huey) meri pairwi karo aur meri Namaz seekh lo."
1217,"Yaqoob bin Abdur-Rehman bin Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin abd , Qaari Qarshi ne kaha : mujhey abu-Hazim ne hadis sunai ke kuchh log Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey, neez Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne abu-Hazim se hadis sunai ke log Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur unse puchha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka member kis ( lakdi ( se ( bana hua) hai. . . . . . .) aagey ( ibne-abi-Hazim ki riwayat ki hadis ki tarah hai."
1218,"Hakam bin-Musa Qintari ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne hadis sunai, neez Abu-Bakar ibne-Abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein abu-Khalid aur abu-Usama ne hadis sunai, un sab ne Hisham se, unhon-ne Muhammad (bin Sirin ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne is baat se mana farmaya ke koi aadmi pahlu par hath rakhey huey Namaz padhey . Imam Muslim ke ustad Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bajaey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke alfaz hain."
1219,"hamein Wakee ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Hisham dustwaai ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Mueqeeb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid mein hath se kankariyaan saaf karne ka tazkira kya aur farmaya : agar tumharey liye usey kiye baghair chaara na ho to aik baar ( kar lo. ("
1220,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Mueqeeb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke logon ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Namaz (ke doran ( mein hath se ( kankariyaan wghaira) saaf karne ke barey mein sawal kya to aap ne farmaya : aik baar (ki ja sakti hain. (
1221,"Khalid-bin Haris ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne isi sanad se hadis sunai aur) (Muaiqeeb sey) ke bajaey) (Muaiqeeb ne hadis sunai) kaha,"
1222,"Hisham ke bajaey) Sheban ne Yahya se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aadmi ke barey mein jo sajdey ki jagah ki mitti barabar karta hai, farmaya : agar tum ne aisa karna hi hai to aik baar karo."
1223,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (masjid ki) qibley wali diwar (ki samt ( mein balgham mila thook laga hua dekha to usey khurch diya, phir logon ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar farmaya : jab tum mein se koi Namaz mein ho to apne samney na thookey kyonke jab wo wo Namaz padhta hai to Allah uske samney hota hai."
1224,"Ubaidullah, Lais-bin-Sad, Ayub, Suhak bin Usman aur Musa-bin-Aqba sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid ke qibley (ki samt) mein balgham dekha. siwaey Suhak ke ke unki riwayat mein (masjid ke qibley ke bajaey) qibley (ki samt) mein ke alfaz hain. . . . .) aagey (Imam Malik ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat hai,"
1225,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid ke qibley (ki samt ( mein balgham dekha to aap ne usey aik kankar ke zariey se khurch daala, phir aap ne is baat se mana farmaya ke koi shakhs apne daain ya samney thookey, albatta wo (agar kachchi zamin ya ret par Namaz padh raha hai to ( apni baain taraf ya baain paon ke nichey thook sakta hai."
1226,"(Sufiyan ke bajaey) Yunus aur Ibrahim ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) donon ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne balgham mila thook dekha. . . . . . . .) aagey ( ibne-Uena ki hadis ki tarah hai."
1227,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Mina se riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qibley ki diwar par thook ya raint ya balgham dekha to khurch dala.
1228,"ibne-Ulaih ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qasim bin Mehran se, unhon-ne abu Raafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid ke qibley (ki samt ( mein balgham dekha to logon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya : tum mein se kisi aik ko kya (ho jata ( hai, wo apne rab ki taraf munh karke khada hota hai, phir apne samney balgham phenk deta hai? kya tum mein se kisi ko ye pasand hai ke uski taraf rukh kya jaey, iske munh ke samney thook diya jaaey? chunanche jab tum mein se koi shakhs khankar phainkna chahey to wo apni baain taraf qadam ke nichey phainkey , agar uski gunjaaish na paaey to aisey kar ley. Qasim ne uski wazaahat main apne kapdey mein thooka, phir iske aik hissey ko doosrey par ragad diya."
1229,"( ibne-Ulaih ke bajaey) Abdul-Waris , Hushaim aur Shoba ne Qasim bin Mehran se hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne abu Raafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ibne-Ulaih ki hadis ki tarah (riwaayat bayan ki.) Hushaim ki hadis mein ye izafa kya : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jaisey mein dekh raha hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kapdey ka aik hissey doosrey par lota ( ragad ( rahe hain. is tarah masjid mein gandagi nahi phailti aur kapdey ko bahar ley ja kar dhoya ja sakta hai"
1230,"(Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi Namaz mein hota hai to wo apne rab se raaz w niyaaz karta hai, isliye wo na apne samney thookey na hi daain taraf, albatta baain taraf paon ke nichey (thook ley)"
1231,abu-Awana ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : masjid mein thookna aik gunah hai aur uska kaffara ye hai ke (agar farsh kachchaa hai to) usey dafn kar diya jaey.
1232,"(abu-Awana ke bajaey) Shoba ne kaha : maine Qatada se masjid mein thookney ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : masjid mein thookna aik gunah hai aur iska kaffara usey dafn karna hai."
1233,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : mere samney meri ummat ke achchhey aur burey aamaal pesh kiye gaey, maine uske achchhey aamaal mein rastey se takleef deh cheez hataaney ko dekha, iske burey aamaal mein balgham ko paya jo masjid mein hota hai aur usey dafn nahi kya jata."
1234,"Kahmas ne Yazeed bin-Abdullah-bin Shikhkhir se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein) Namaz ada ki, maine aapko dekha ke aap ne ( galley se) balgham nikala aur) chunkey paon ke nichey ret thi us liye) usey apne jootey se masal diya."
1235,Jurairi ne abul-Ala Yazeed bin-Abdullah-bin Shikhkhir se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi. kaha : aap ne galey se balgham nikala aur usey apne baain jootey se masal dala.
1236,"Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne hamein abu-Muslima Saeed bin Yazeed se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jootey pahan kar Namaz padhtey they? unhon-ne jawab diya : haan."
1237,"(Bishr ke bajaey) Ibad bin Awam ne kaha : hamein abu-Muslima Saeed bin Yazeed ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya. . . . .) aagey ( pehli riwayat ki tarah hai."
1238,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bel-booton wali aik naqshdaar chadar mein Namaz padhi aur farmaya : iske bel-booton ne mujhey mashghool kar diya tha, usey abu-jaham ke paas ley jao aur (iske badley ( mujhey anbajani chadar la do."
1239,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik bel-booton wali naqshdar chadar par Namaz padhney ke liye khadey huey to uske naqsh w nigaar par aap ki nazar padi, jab aap apni Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : ye naqshdar chadar abu-jaham bin Huzefa ke paas ley jao aur mujhey uski ( saada ( anbajaani chadar laa do kyonke us ne abhi meri Namaz se meri tawajjoh hata di thi."
1240,"( ibne-Shahab Zohri ke bajaey) Hisham ne apne walid Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Mina se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik naqshdaar chadar thi jis par bel-bootey baney huey they, Namaz mein aap ka khayal uski taraf chala jata tha, aap ne wo abu-jaham ko de di aur uski ( bel-booton ke baghair saada ( anbajani chadar us se ley li. (ye chadar aazar bejaan ke aik Shahar anbajan ki taraf mansub thi.)"
1241,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jab raat ka khana aa jaey aur Namaz ke liye takbeer ( bhi) keh di jaey to pahley khana kha lo."
1242,"Amr (bin Haaris) ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab raat ka khana pesh kar diya jaey aur Namaz ka ( bhi) waqt ho jaey to maghrib ki Namaz padhney se pahley khaney ki shuruaat karo aur (namaz ke liye) apna raat ka khana chhodne mein ujlat na karo. (is zamaney mein raat ka khana maghrib ke qareeb hi khaya jata tha. ("
1243,"ibne-Numair, Hafs aur Wakee ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke waastey se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki jis tarah ibne-Uena ne Zohri se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan ki."
1244,saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ke samney Sham (Syria) ka khana rakha jaey idhar Namaz khadi ho to pahley khana kha ley aur Namaz ke liye jaldi na karey jab tak khaney se farigh na ho.''
1245,"Musa-bin-Aqba, ibne-Juraij aur Ayub sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uper zikr ki gaee riwayat ki tarah riwayat bayan ki."
1246,"Hatim bin Ismail ne ( abu Hazra ( Yaqoob bin Mujahid se, unhon-ne ibne-abi-Atiq ( Abdullah-bin Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr siddeeq ( se riwayat ki, kaha : maine aur Qasim (bin Muhammad-bin abi-Bakr siddeeq ( ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas ( baithey huey) guftgu ki. Qasim zaban ki shadeed ghaltiyaan karne waley insan they, wo aik kaneez ke betey they, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Mina ne us se kaha : kya baat hai tum mere us bhatijey ki tarah kyon guftgu nahi kartey? haan, main janti hun (tum mein) ye baat kahan se aai hai, usko uski maan ne adab (guftgu ka tareeqa) sikhaya aur tumhen tumhari maan ne sikhaya. is par Qasim naraz ho gaey aur unke khilaf dil mein ghussa kya, phir jab unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ka dasterkhaan aatey dekha to uth khadey huey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : kahan jatey ho? unhon-ne kaha : main Namaz padhney laga hun. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : baith jao . unhon-ne kaha : maine Namaz padhni hai. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : baith jao, dhokey baaz ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : khana samney aa jaey to Namaz nahi. aur na wo ( shakhs Namaz padhey ( jis par peshab paakhaane ki zarurat ghalib aa rahi ho."
1247,"Ismail bin Jafar ne kaha : mujhey abu Hazra al-Qaas ne Abdullah-bin-abi-Ateeq se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Mina se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur hadis mein Qasim ka waqia bayan na kya."
1248,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Zuhair-bin-Harab donon ne kaha : Yahya qattaan ne hamein Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ghazwae-Khaibar ke mauqe par farmaya : jisne us paudey, aap ki murad lehsun tha, main se kuchh khaya ho wo masjidon mein hargiz na aaey. Zuhair ne sirf jang kaha, khaibar ka naam nahi liya."
1249,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : ham se Ubaidullah ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne us tarkaari mein se kuchh khaya ho wo hamari masjidon ke qareeb na aaey yahan tak ke uski boo chali jaey. aap ki murad lehsun se thi."
1250,"Abdul-Azeez se, jo Suheb ke betey hain, riwayat hai ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se lehsun ke barey mein puchha gaya to unhon-ne jawab diya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne us paudey mein se kuchh khaya ho wo hargiz hamarey qareeb na aaey aur na hamarey sath Namaz padhey."
1251,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne us paudey mein se kuchh khaya ho wo hargiz hamari masjid ke qareeb na aaey aur na hamein lehsun ki bu se takleef de.
1252,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne piyaz aur gandana khaney se mana farmaya, so (eik martaba) ham zarurat se majbur ho gaey aur unhein kha liya to aap ne farmaya : jisne us badboodar sabzi mein se kuchh khaya ho wo hargiz hamari masjid ke qareeb na aaey, Farishtey bhi yaqinan us cheez se takleef mehsus kartey hain jis se insan takleef mehsus kartey hain."
1253,"abu-Taahir aur Hurmala ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Ata-bin-abi-Ribah ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Hurmala ki riwayat mein hai, un ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) ko yaqin tha. ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne lehsun ya piyaz khaya wo ham se door rahe ya hamari masjidon se door rahe aur apne ghar baithey aur aisa hua ke (eik baar (aap ke paas aik handi laai gaee jis mein kuchh har tarkariyan thin, aap ne unse kuchh bo mehsus ki to unke mutaalliq poochha. aapko un tarkariyon ke barey mein bataya gaya jo usmein ( dali gai) thin to aap ne usey , apne sathiyon mein se aik ke paas ley janey ko kaha, jab usne bhi usey dekh kar (aap ki na-pasandidgi ki bina par) usko na-pasand kya to aap ne farmaya : tum kha lo kyonke main unse sargoshi karta hun jin se tum sargoshi nahi kartey ho. (is se Farishtey murad hain. sahi ibne- Khuzaima aur sahi ibne-Hibban ki riwayat mein is baat ki sarahat maujood hai.)"
1254,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Ata ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne ye tarkari lehsun khaya aur aik baar farmaya : jisne piyaz , lehsun aur gandana khaya. to wo hargiz hamari masjid ke qareeb na aaey kyonke Farishtey ( bhi) un chizon se aziyat mehsus kartey hain jin se Adam ke betey aziyat mehsus kartey hain."
1255,"Muhammad-bin-Bakr aur Abdur-Razzaq ne ( 2 mukhtalif sanadon se riwayat kartey huey) kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne usi (pichhli (sanad ke sath khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne is paudey, aap ki murad lehsun se thi, main se kuchh khaya ho wo hamari masjid mein hamarey paas na aaey aur unhon (ibne-Juraij ( ne piyaz aur gandne ka zikr nahi kya."
1256,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ham khaibar ki fateh se farigh nahi huey they ke ham, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathi , us tarkari, lehsun, par ja padey, log bhookey they aur ham ne usey khub achi tarah khaya, phir ham masjid ki taraf gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne boo-mahsoos ki. aap ne farmaya : jisne us badbudar paudey mein se kuchh khaya hai wo masjid mein hamarey qareeb na aaey. is par log kehney lagey : (lehsun) haram ho gaya, haram ho gaya. ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to aap ne farmaya : aey logo! aisi cheez ko haram karna mere hath mein nahi jisey Allah ne mere liye halal kar diya hai lekin ye aisa pauda hai jiski bu mujhey na-pasand hai."
1257,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba (eik baar ( piyaz ke aik khet ke paas se guzrey . unmein se kuchh log utrey aur is mein se kuchh kha liya, aur dusron ne na khaya. ham aap ke paas gaey to aap ne un logon ko) qareeb ( bula liya jinhoney piyaz nahi khaya tha aur doosrey (jinhon ne piyaz khaya tha) unhein peechhey kar diya yahan tak ke uski bu khatm ho gaee."
1258,"Hisham ne kaha : ham se Qatada ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Madaan bin abi Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Jumey ke din khutba diya aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka tazkira kya, kaha : maine khuwab dekha hai, jaisey aik murgh ne mujhey teen thongein mari hain aur usko main apni maut qareeb aaney ke siwa aur kuchh nahi samajhta aur kuchh qabaayel mujh se mutalba kar rahe hain ke main kisi ko apna jaa-nasheen bana dun. bila shubah Allah Taala apne Deen ko zaaye nahi honey dega, na apni khilafat ko aur na us shariiat ko jiske sath us ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maboos farmaya, agar mujhey jald maut aa jaey to khilafat in 6 hazraat ke aapsi mashwarey se tay hogi jin se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni wafat ke waqt khush they. aur main janta hun ke kuchh log jinko maine Islam ki khaatir apne is hath se maara hai, wo is baat ( khilafat ( par aetraz karengey, agar wo aisa karengey to wo Allah ke dushman , kaafir aur gumrah hongey, phir main apne baad jo ( hal talab ( cheezein chhod kar ja raha hun unmein se mere nazdeek kalaala ki wiraasat ke masley se badh kar koi masla zyada aham nahi. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kisi masley ke barey mein itni baar rujoo nahi kya jitni baar kalaala ke barey mein kya aur aap ne ( bhi) mere sath kisi masley mein is qadr sakhti nahi barti jitni mere sath aap ne is masley mein sakhti ki yahan tak ke aap ne ungli mere seeney mein chubho kar farmaya : aey umr ! kya garmi ke mausam mein utarney wali aayat tumharey liye kafi nahi jo sura Nisa ke aakhir mein hai? mein agar zinda raha to main is masley ( kalaala (ke barey mein aisa faisla karunga ke (har insan ( jo Quran padhta hai ya nahi padhta hai iske mutabiq faisla kar sakega , phir aap ne farmaya : aey Allah ! main shehron ke governaron ke barey mein tujhey gawah banata hun ke maine logon par unhein sirf isliye muqarrar karke bheja ke wo unse insaf karein aur logon ko unke Deen aur unke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat ki taleem dein aur unke amwaal fai unmein taqseem karein aur agar logon ke maamlaat mein unhein koi mushkil pesh aaey to usey mere samney pesh karein. phir aey logo ! tum 2 paudey khaatey ho, main unhein (bu ke eitibaar se) burey paudey hi samajhta hun, ye piyaz aur lehsun hain. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, jab masjid mein aapko kisi aadmi se unki bo aati to aap usey Baqee ki taraf nikal dene ka hukm saadir farmatey, isliye jo shakhs unhein khana chahta hai wo unhein pakaakar unki bu mar de."
1259,Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba aur Shoba ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
1260,"ibne- Wahab ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hewa se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne shaddaad-bin haad ke aazad karda ghulam abu Abdullah se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs kisi aadmi ko masjid mein kisi gum shuda janwar ke barey mein elaan kartey huey suney to wo kahey : Allah tumhara janwar tumhen na lautaaey kyonke masjidein is kaam ke liye nahi banai gain."
1261,(ibne-Wahab ke bajaey) muqri ne Hewa se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
1262,"Sufiyan Sory ne hamein khabar di, unhon-ne Alqama bin-Marsad se, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Barida se aur unhon-ne apne walid ( Barida bin Hasib Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne masjid mein elaan kya aur kaha : jo surkh oont (ki nishaandehi (ke liye awaz dega. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaney lagey : tujhey ( tera oont ( na miley, masjidein sirf unhi kaamon ke liye banai gaee hain jinke liye unhein banaya gaya. (yani ibadat aur Allah ke zikr ke liye. ("
1263,"abu Sanan ne Alqama bin Marsad se, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Barida se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke (eik baar ( jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai to aik aadmi ne khadey ho kar kaha : jo surkh oont (ki nishaandehi) ke liye awaz dega. to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ( apna oont ( na paogey, masaajid sirf unhi kaamon ke liye banai gaee hain jinke liye unhein banaya gaya."
1264,"Muhammad-bin Sheba ne Alqama bin-Marsad se, unhon-ne ( Sulaiman (bin Barida se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke jab Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz padh chukey to aik badwi aaya aur masjid ke darwazey se apna sar andar kya. . . . . . phir un donon ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya. Imam Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : Muhammad-bin Sheba se murad abu Naama Sheba bin Naama hai jis se Misar , Hushaim , Jarir aur doosrey koofi rawiyon ne riwayat ki."
1265,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah tum mein se koi jab Namaz padhney ke liye khada hota hai to shaitan aa kar usey shube mein daalta hai yahan tak ke wo nahi janta ke usne kitni (rakatein) padhi hain. tum mein se koi jab ye (kaifiyat) paaey to wo (aakhiri tashahud mein) baithey huey 2 sajdey kar ley."
1266,Sufiyan-bin-Uena aur Lais-bin-Sad ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki hai.
1267,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se riwayat hai, kaha : hamein abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis sunai ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab azan kahi jati hai to shaitan peeth pher kar bhaagta hai gooz mar raha hota hai taake azan (ki awaz ( na suney . jab azan khatm ho jati hai to ( wapas ( aata hai, phir jab Namaz ke liye takbeer kahi jati hai to peeth pher kar bhag jata hai, jab takbeer khatm ho jati hai to aa jata hai taake insan aur uske dil ke darmyan khayal aaraai shuru karwaaey , wo kehta hai : falan baat yad karo, falan cheez yad karo. wo cheezein ( usey yad karaata hai) jo usey yad nahi hotin yahan tak ke wo shakhs yun ho jata hai ke usey yad nahi rehta us ne kitni rakatein padhi hain, chunanche jab tum mein se kisi ko yad na rahe ke usne kitni rakatein padhi hain to wo ( tashahud mein) baithey baithey 2 sajdey kar ley."
1268,Abdur-Rehman Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Namaz ke liye takbeer kahi jati hai to shaitan peeth pher kar gooz maarta hua bhaagta hai. . . . . . aagey uper ki riwayat ki tarah zikr kya aur ye izafa kya : usey raghbat aur ummeed dilata hai aur usey uski aisi zarooratein yad dilata hai jo usey yad nahi hotin.
1269,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Buhaina (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein kisi aik Namaz ki 2 rakatein padhaain, phir ( teesri ke liye) khadey ho gaey aur) darmyan ke tashahud ke liye) na baithey to log bhi aap ke sath khadey ho gaey, jab aap ne Namaz poori kar li aur ham aap ke salam ke intizar mein they, to aap ne takbeer kahi aur baithey baithey salam se pahley 2 sajdey kiye, phir salam pher diya."
1270,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Buhaina Asadi (Raziallahu anhu) se, jo banu- abdul-Muttalib ke haleef they, riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz mein, jab aapko (doosri rakaat ke baad) baithna tha, khadey ho gaey, phir jab aap ne apni Namaz mukammal kar li to aap ne baithey baithey har sajdey ke liye takbeer kehtey huey salam se pahley 2 sajdey kiye, aur logon ne bhi) tashahud ke liye) baithney ki jagah, jo aap bhool gaey they, aap ke sath 2 sajdey kiye."
1271,"(ibne-Shahab ke bajaey) Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Malik ibne- Buhaina Azdi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 rakaton ke baad jahan Namaz mein aap ka baithney ka irada tha, (wahan) khadey ho gaey, aap ne apni Namaz jari rakhi . phir jab Namaz ke aakhir mein pahunchey to salam se pahley sajdey kiye, uske baad salam phera."
1272,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ko apni Namaz mein shak ho jaey aur usey malum na ho ke usne kitni rakatein padh li hain? teen ya char ? to wo shak ko chhod de aur jitni rakaton par usey yaqin hai un par buniyad rakhey ( teen yaqeeni hain to chothi padh ley ( phir salam se pahley 2 sajdey kar ley , agar us ne panch rakatein padh li hain to ye sajdey uski Namaz ko juft ( chh rakatein ( kar dengey aur agar us ne char ki takmeel kar li thi to ye sajdey shaitan ki zillat w ruswai ka baais hongey."
1273,Dawud bin Qais ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur uske mana ke mutabiq ye kaha : wo ( namazi ( salam pherney se pahley 2 sajdey kar ley. jis tarah Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne kaha.
1274,"Jarir ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se aur unhon-ne Alqama se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhai. Ibrahim ne kaha : aap ne usmein zyadti ya kami kar di. phir jab aap ne salam phera to aap se puchha gaya : aey Allah ke rasool! kya Namaz mein koi nai cheez (tabdeeli) aa gaee hai? aap ne puchha : wo kiya? sahaba ne kaha : aap ne itni itni rakatein padhai hain. ( rawi ne kaha : (aap ne apne paon modey , qible ki taraf rukh kya aur 2 sajdey kiye, phir salam phera , phir aap ne hamari taraf rukh kya aur farmaya : agar Namaz mein koi nai baat hoti to main tumhen bata deta , lekin main aik insan hun, jis tarah tum bhooltey ho main bhi bhool jata hun, isliye jab main bhool jaun to mujhey yad dila diya karo aur jab tum mein se kisi ko apni Namaz ke barey mein shak ho jaey to wo sahi ki justju karey aur uske mutabiq (namaz ki) takmeel karey, phir ( saho ke) 2 sajdey kar ley."
1275,ibne-Bishr aur Wakee donon ne Misar se aur unhon-ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki ibne-Bishr ki riwayat mein hai : wo ghaur karey ke usmein se sihat ke qareeb tar kiya hai? aur Wakee ki riwayat mein hai : wo sahi ( sura ko yad karne) ki justju kare.
1276,Wuhaib bin Khalid ne kaha : hamein Mansoor ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. Mansoor ne kaha : wo ghaur karey ke usmein sihat ke qareeb tar kya hai.
1277,Sufiyan ne Mansoor se mazkura (uper zikr) sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki aur kaha : wo sahi ki justju kare.
1278,Shoba ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki aur kaha : usmein jo sahi ke qareeb tar hai uski justju kare.
1279,Fuzel bin Ayaz ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath khabar di aur kaha : wo uski justju karey jisey wo sahi samajhta hai.
1280,Abdul-Azeez bin Abdus-Samad ne Mansoor se un sab rawiyon ki sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki aur kaha : wo sahi ki justju kare.
1281,"Hakam ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Alqama se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz ( mein) panch rakaat padha dein, jab aap ne salam phera to aap se puchha gaya : kya Namaz mein izafa kar diya gaya hai? aap ne farmaya : wo kya hai? sahaba ne kaha : aap ne panch rakaat padhi hain. to aap ne 2 sajdey kiye."
1282,"ibne-Numair ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Idris ne Hasan-bin- Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim (bin Suwed ( se aur unhon-ne Alqama se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein panch rakaat padhaain."
1283,"Usman bin abi Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki. lafz unhi ke hain. unhon-ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Hasan-bin- Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim bin Suwed se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Alqama ne Zohar ki panch rakatein padha din. jab unhon-ne salam phera to logon ne kaha : abu shibl! aap ne panch rakatein padhai hain. unhon-ne kaha : bilkul nahi, maine aisa nahi kya. logon ne kaha : kyon nahi ! (aap ne aisa hi kya hai.) Ibrahim ne kaha : main logon ke kinarey ( waley hissey ( mein tha aur bachcha tha, maine kaha : haan! aap ne panch rakatein padhi hain. unhon-ne mujh se kaha : aik aankh waley! to bhi yahi kehta hai? maine kaha : ji haan ! to wo mudey aur 2 sajdey kiye, phir salam phera, phir kaha : Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (bin Masood) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein panch rakatein padha din, jab aap mudey to logon ne aapas mein khusur-phusar shuru kar di. aap ne puchha : tumhen kya hua hai? unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya Namaz mein izafa kar diya gaya hai? aap ne farmaya : nahi. logon ne kaha : aap ne panch rakatein padhai hain. to aap paltey, phir 2 sajdey kiye, phir salam phera, phir farmaya : main tumhari hi tarah ka insan hun, main (bhi) bhool jata hun jis tarah tum log bhool jatey ho. ibne-Numair ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kya : jab tum mein se koi bhool jaey to wo 2 sajdey kar ley."
1284,"Abdur-Rehman bin Aswad ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein panch rakatein padha din to ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya Namaz mein izafa kar diya gaya hai? aap ne farmaya : wo kiya? sahaba ne kaha : aap ne panch rakaat padhai hain. aap ne farmaya : main tumhari tarah insan hun, main bhi isi tarah yad rakhta hun, jis tarah tum yad rakhtey ho aur main (bhi) isi tarah bhool jata hun, jis tarah tum bhool jatey ho. phir aap ne saho ke 2 sajdey kiye."
1285,"(Ali) bin Mus-hir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Alqama se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai aur is mein kuchh izafa kar diya. Ibrahim ne kaha ke haan, waham mujhey hua hai, Alqama ko nahi. kaha gaya : Allah ke rasool! kya Namaz mein izafa kar diya gaya hai? aap ne farmaya : main tumhari tarah insan hi hun, main bhi bhoolta hun, jaisey tum bhooltey ho, isliye jab tum mein se koi bhool jaey to wo baithey baithey 2 sajdey kar ley. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukh (qible ki taraf) phera aur 2 sajdey kiye."
1286,"Hafs aur abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se baqi bachi is sanad ke sath Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam aur guftgu ke baad saho ke 2 sajdey kiye."
1287,"Zayda ne Sulaiman (Aamash) se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi, aap ne zyada padha di thi ya kam . Ibrahim ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! ye ( waham) meri taraf se hai. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya Namaz mein koi nayaa hukm aa gaya hai? aap ne farmaya : nahi to ham ne aapko jo aap ne kya tha us se aagah kya to aap ne farmaya : jab aadmi zyadti ya kami kar ley to 2 sajdey kare. ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : iske baad aap ne 2 sajdey kiye."
1288,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha : ham se Ayub ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Muhammad-bin Sirin se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne do-pahar ke baad ki aik namaze-Zohar ya Asr padhai aur 2 rakaton ke baad salam pher diya, phir qibley ki samt (khadey huey) kajhoor ke aik taney ke paas aaey aur ghussey ki kaifiyat mein us se tek laga li. logon mein Abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ‌ ( bhi) maujood they, unhon-ne aap ki haibat ki bina par guftgu na ki jabke jald baaz log (namaz padhtey hi ( nikal gaey, aur kehney lagey : Namaz mein kami ho gaee hai. to zul-yadain ( naam ke shakhs) khada hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya Namaz mukhtasar kar di gaee hai ya aap bhool gaey hain? Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne daain aur baain dekh kar puchha : zul-yadain kya keh raha hai? logon ne kaha : sach keh raha hai, aap ne 2 rakatein hi padhi hain. chunanche aap ne 2 rakatein ( mazeed ( padhein aur salam pher diya, phir ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha aur sajda kya, phir ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha aur sar uthaya , phir ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha aur sajda kya, phir ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha aur sar uthaya .) Muhammad-bin Sirin ne) kaha : Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se mujhey bataya gaya ke unhon-ne kaha : aur salam phera ."
1289,"( Sufiyan ke bajaey) Hammad ne hamein hadis bayan ki (kaha : ( hamein Ayub ne Muhammad-bin Sirin se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein dopahar ke baad ki 2 namazon mein se aik Namaz padhai. . . . . . aagey Sufiyan (bin Uena (ke ham mana hadis (sunai)"
1290,"ibne-abi Ahmed ke aazad karda ghulam abu Sufiyan se riwayat hai ke usne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Asr ki Namaz padhai aur 2 rakaton mein salam pher diya. zul-yadain ( naam ke shakhs) khada hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Namaz kam kar di gaee hai ya aap bhool gaey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aisa koi kaam nahi hua. usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! koi aik kaam to hua hai. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur puchha : kya zul-yadain ne sach kaha? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan ! aey Allah ke rasool! to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo Namaz reh gaee thi poori ki, phir baithey baithey salam pherney ke baad 2 sajdey kiye."
1291,"Ali bin-Mubarak ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Yahya ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Salma ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ki 2 rakaatein padhaain, phir salam pher diya to banu-Sulaim ka aik aadmi aap ke qareeb aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Namaz kam kar di gaee hai ya aap bhool gaey hain? . . . . . . aur aagey (pichhli ( hadis bayan ki."
1292,"Sheban ne Yahya se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( iqtida (pairvi) mein) Zohar ki Namaz padh raha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaton par salam pher diya, is par bani-Sulaim ka aik aadmi khada hua. . . . . . . aagey ( uper zikr ki gaee ( hadis bayan ki"
1293,"Ismail bin Ibrahim ne Khalid ( Haza ( se, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne abu Muhallab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ki Namaz padhai aur teen rakaat par salam pher diya, phir apne ghar tashrif le gaey to aik aadmi jisey khirbaaq kaha jata tha aur uske hath lambey they, wo aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jo ( saho ( hua tha uska aap ke samney tazkira kya, aap ghussey ki haalat mein, chadar ghaseet'tey huey nikley yahan tak ke logon ke paas aa pahunchey aur puchha : kya ye sach keh raha hai? logon ne kaha : ji haan ! to aap ne aik rakaat padhai, phir salam phera, phir saho ke 2 sajdey kiye, phir salam phera."
1294,"abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne Khalid Haza se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ki teesri rakaat mein salam pher diya, phir uth kar apne hujrey mein dakhil ho gaey, aik ( lambey ( chaudey hathon wala aadmi khada hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya Namaz kam kar di gaee hai? phir aap ghussey ke aalim mein nikley aur chhodi hui rakaat padhai , phir salam pher diya, phir saho ke 2 sajdey kiye, phir salam phera ."
1295,"Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Quran Majeed ki tilawat farmaya kartey they. aap is sura ki tilawat farmatey jis mein sajda hota aur sajda kartey to ham (sab ( bhi aap ke sath sajda kartey, yahan tak ke ham mein se kuchh ko peshani rakhney ke liye bhi jagah na milti thi."
1296,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : kabhi-kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Quran padhtey huey sajdey ( wali aayat ( se guzartey to hamarey sath sajda kartey, aap ke paas hamari bheed lag jati yahan tak ke ham mein se kuchh ko sajda karne ke liye jagah na milti (ye sajda ( Namaz ke ilawa hota tha."
1297,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sura najam ki tilawat ki aur is mein sajda kya aur aap ke sath jitney log they sab ne sajda kya, magar aik boodhey (Umayya-bin-Khalaf) ne kankariyon ya mitti ki aik muththi bhar kar apni peshani se laga li aur kaha : mere liye yahi kafi hai. Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : maine baad mein dekha, usey kufr ki haalat mein qatl kya gaya."
1298,Ata-bin-Yasar ne (apne shagird ibne- qaseet ko) bataya ke unhon-ne imam ke sath ( Quran ki kisi sura ki) qirat karne ke barey mein Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kiya? unhon-ne kaha : imam ke sath ( Fatiha ke siwa ( kuchh na padhey aur kaha : unhon ( Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ( والنجم اذا ھویٰ ( padhi to aap ne sajda na kya.
1299,"Aswad bin Sufiyan ke aazad karda ghulam Abdullah-bin Yazeed ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke samney sura ( اذا السمآ ء النشقت ( padhi aur is mein sajda kya, phir jab salam phera to unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is sura mein sajda kya tha."
1300,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki."
1301,"Ata-bin Mina ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sura Inshiqaq aur Sura Iqra mein sajda kya."
1302,"Safwaan-bin-Sulaim ne banu- makhzoom ke aazad karda ghulam Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Sura Inshiqaq) aur (Sura iqra) mein sajda kya."
1303,"Ubaidullah bin abi Jafar ne Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah bayan kya."
1304,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz Anbari aur Muhammad-bin Abdul-Aala ne kaha : hamein Motamir ne apne walid (Sulaiman Taimi) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Bakr ( bin-Abdullah Muzni ( se aur unhon-ne abu Raafe se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath isha ki Namaz padhi to unhon-ne (Sura Inshqaq) ki tilawat ki aur is mein sajda kya. maine puchha : ye sajda kaisa hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : maine usmein abul-Qaasim ( Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke peechhey sajda kya, isliye main usmein hamesha sajda karta rahunga yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ja milun. ( Muhammad (bin Abdul-Aala ne kaha : main bhi hamesha ye sajda karta hun."
1305,"Esa-bin-Yonus , Yazeed bin Zaree aur Saleem bin akhzar sab ne ( Sulaiman ( Taimi se pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki lekin unhon-ne ( Khalaf abi al-Qasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ( abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey (ke alfaz nahi kahey ."
1306,"Shoba ne Ataa-bin-abi-Memoona se unhon-ne abu Raafe se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, wo (Sura Inshiqaq) mein sajda kartey they. maine puchha : aap usmein sajda kartey hain? unhon-ne kaha : haan ! maine apne khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko usmein sajda kartey dekha, isliye main hamesha usmein sajda karta rahunga yahan tak ke unse ja milun . Shoba ne kaha : maine ( ata se) puchha : ( khaleel se murad ( Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain? unhon-ne kaha : haan."
1307,"Usman bin-Hakam ne kaha : Aamir bin-Abdullah-bin Zuber ne apne walid se riwayat kartey huey mujhey hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz mein baithtey to apna bayan paon apni raan aur apni pindlii ke darmyan kar letey aur apna dayan paon bichha letey aur apna bayan hath apne baain ghutney par aur apna dayan hath apni daain raan par rakh letey aur apni ungli se ishara kartey."
1308,"ibne- Ajlan ne Aamir bin-Abdullah-bin Zuber se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab (namaz mein) baith kar dua kartey to apna dayan hath apni daain raan par aur apna bayan hath apni baain raan par rakhtey aur apni shahadat ki ungli se ishara kartey aur apna angoothaa apni darmiyani ungli par rakhtey aur baain ghutney ko apni baain hatheli ke andar ley letey ( pakad letey. ("
1309,"Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz mein baithtey to apne donon hath apne donon ghutnon par rakh letey aur angoothey se milney wali daaein hath ki ungli ( shahadat ki ungli) utha kar us se dua kartey aur us haalat mein aapka bayan hath aapkey baain ghutney par hota, usey (aap (us ( ghutney ( par phailaey hotey ."
1310,Ayub ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab tashahud mein baithtey to apna bayan hath apne baain ghutney par rakhtey aur apna dayan hath apne daain ghutney par rakhtey aur ungliyon se tirpan ( 53 ( ki girah banatey aur angusht shahadat se ishara kartey.
1311,Imam Malik ne Muslim-bin abi Maryam se aur unhon-ne Ali-bin Abdur-Rehman Muaawi se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha ke main Namaz ke doran (be khayaali ke aalim mein nichey padi hui ( kankariyon se khel raha tha. jab unhon-ne salam phera to mujhey mana kya aur kaha : waisey karo jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya kartey they. maine puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya kartey they? unhon-ne bataya : jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz mein baithtey to apni daain hatheli apni daain raan par rakhtey aur sab ungliyon ko band kar letey aur angoothey ke sath wali ungli se ishara kartey aur apni baain hatheli ko apni baain raan par rakhtey.
1312,"ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Muslim-bin abi Maryam se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Ali-bin Abdur-Rehman Muaawi se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath khadey ho kar Namaz padhi. . . phir Sufiyan ne Malik ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur) Sufiyan ke shagird ibne-abi-Umar ne) ye izafa kya ke Sufiyan ne kaha : Yahya-bin-Saeed ne hamein ye hadis Muslim (bin abi Maryam ( se bayan ki thi, phir Muslim (bin abi Maryam ( ne khud mujhey ye hadis sunai."
1313,"Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne hukm aur Mansoor se, unhon-ne Mujahid se aur unhon-ne abu Mamar se riwayat ki ke aik Hakim jo Makka mein tha 2 taraf salam phertaa tha. Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : wo kahan se us sunnat se waabastaa hua hai? Hakam ne apni hadis mein kaha : (Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aisey hi kya kartey they."
1314,"Ahmad-bin-Hanbal ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Shoba se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne abu Mamar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. Shoba ne kaha, Hakam ne aik baar ye riwayat marfoo bayan ki. ke aik Hakim ya aik aadmi ne 2 taraf salam phera to Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha is ne ye ( sunnat ( kahan se apna li hai? maano us door ke haakimon ne aisi sunnatein bhi tark ki hui thin. jisne ehtimaam kya sahaba ne usey saraahaa . muhaddeseen ki kaawishon se ye sab sunnatein zinda huin."
1315,"Aamir-bin-Sad ne apne walid ( Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apni daain aur baain taraf salam phertey dekha karta tha yahan tak ke main aap ke rukhsaron ki safedi dekhta tha."
1316,"Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr (bin Dinar ( se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu Mabad ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Mina se is baat ki khabar di, baad main ( bhool janey ki wjah se) us se inkar kar diya, unhon (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ke hamein Rasulullah ki Namaz khatm honey ka pata takbeer se chalta tha."
1317,"ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr-bin-Dinar se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula abu Mabad ko Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se bataatey huey suna, unhon (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz khatm ho janey ka pata Allahu-akbar hi se lagta tha. Amr ne kaha : maine is riwayat ka ( baad mein) abu Mabad ke samney zikr kya to unhon-ne us se inkar kya aur kaha : maine tumhen ye hadis nahi sunai. Amr ne kaha : halanke unhon-ne us se pahley mujhey ye baat batai thi."
1318,ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne bataya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu Mabad ne unhein bataya ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke jab log farz Namaz se salam phertey to iske baad buland awaz se zikr karna Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur main ( raaij ( tha aur) abu Mabad ne) kaha : Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jab log salam phertey to mujhey is baat ka ilm usi (buland awaz ke sath kiye gaey zikr) se hota tha.
1319,"Urwa-bin-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey jabke mere paas aik Yahudi aurat maujood thi aur wo keh rahi thi : kya tumhen pata hai ke qabron main tumhara imtihan hoga? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaufzada ho gaey aur farmaya : yahood hi ki aazmaish hogi. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne batlaya : kuchh din guzarney ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tumhen pata chala mujhey wahi ki gaee hai ke tum qabron mein aazmaey jaogey? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko suna, aap azaabe-qabr se panah maangtey they."
1320,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke maine ( Yahudi aurat waale) us ( waqiey (ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap qabr ke azab se panah maangtey they."
1321,"abu-Waail (Shaqeeq bin Salma) ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Madina ke yahudiyon ki boodhi aurton mein se do boodhiyan mere ghar aain aur unhon-ne kaha : qabron walon ko unki qabron mein azab diya jata hai. maine un donon ko jhutlaaya aur unki tasdeeq ke liye haan tak kehna gawara na kya, wo chali gain aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey to maine aap se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! mere paas Madina ki boodhi Yahudi aurton mein se do boodhiyan aai thin, unka khayal tha ke qabr walon ko unki qabron mein azab diya jata hai. aap ne ( kuchh din guzar ne ke baad) farmaya : un donon ne sach kaha tha. (qabron mein) un (kaafiron, gunah gaaron) ko aisa azab hota hai ke usey maweshi bhi suntey hain. iske baad maine aapko dekha aap har Namaz mein qabr ke azab se panah maangtey they."
1322,abu-Waail ke bajaey) Ashas ke walid (abu-Shasa Saleem mahaaribi) ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se uper zikr ki gaee hadis riwayat ki. aur is mein ye hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aap ne iske baad jo Namaz bhi padhi maine aap se suna ke aap usmein qabr ke azab se panah maangtey they.
1323,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apni Namaz mein, dajjal ke fitney se panah maangtey suna."
1324,"Wakee ne kaha : hamein Auzai ne Hassan bin Atiya se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin abi Aaisha se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez ( Auzai ne) Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi tashahud padh ley to char chizon se Allah ki panah talab kare. aey Allah ! main jahannam ke azab se aur qabr ke azab se aur zindagi aur maut mein aazmaish se aur Masih dajjal ke fitney ke shar se teri panah mein aata hun."
1325,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz mein (ye ( dua maangtey they : aey Allah ! main qabr ke azab se teri panah chahta hun aur Masih dajjal ke fitney se teri panah ka taalib hun, main zindagi aur maut ke fitney se teri panah mangta hun, aey Allah ! main gunah aur qarz (main phans janey se teri panah chahta hun.) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : kisi kehney waley ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aap qarz se kis qadr panah maangtey hain ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jab aadmi maqrooz ho jaey to baat karta hai to jhoot boltaa hai aur wada karta hai to uski khilaf warzi karta hai"
1326,"Waleed bin Muslim ne kaha : mujhey Auzai ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hassan bin Atiya ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Muhammad-bin abi Aaisha ne hadis sunai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi aakhiri tashahud se farigh ho jaey to char chizon se Allah Taala ki panah talab karey : jahannam ke azab se, qabr ke azab se zindagi aur maut ki aazmaish se aur Masih dajjal ke shar se."
1327,"Haql bin Ziyad aur Esa-bin-Yonus donon ne Auzai ki mazkura (uper zikr) sanad se yahi hadis riwayat ki, usmein hai, aap ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi tashahud se farigh ho. padhi. unhon-ne ( الآخر ( (aakhiri tashahud) ke alfaz nahi kahey."
1328,"Hisham ne Yahya se aur unhon-ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they : Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki : aey Allah ! main qabr ke azab se teri panah mein aata hun aur aag ke azab se aur zindagi aur maut ki aazmaish se aur Masih dajjal ke shar se."
1329,"Amr (bin Dinar ( ne Taaus se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ke azab se Allah ki panah talab karo, qabr ke azab se Allah ki panah maango , Masih dajjal ke fitney se Allah ki panah talab karo aur zindagi aur maut ke fitney se Allah ki panah maango ."
1330,"Taaus ke betey ( Abdullah ( ne apne walid Taaus se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki."
1331,Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki.
1332,"Abdullah-bin Shaqiq ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabr ke azab se, jahannam ke azab se aur dajjal ke fitney se panah maanga kartey they."
1333,"Taaus ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un (sab sahaba ( ko us dua ki taleem isi tarah detey they jis tarah unhein Quran Majeed ki kisi sura ki taleem detey they. aap farmatey they : sab kaho : aey Allah ! ham jahannam ke azab se teri panah maangtey hain aur main qabr ke azab se teri panah mangta hun aur Masih dajjal ke fitney se teri panah mangta hun aur zindagi aur maut ke fitney se teri panah mangta hun. Imam Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : mujhey ye baat pahunchi ke Taaus ne apne betey se puchha : kya tum ne apni Namaz mein ye dua mangi hai? us ne jawab diya : nahi. is par Taaus ne kaha : dobara Namaz padho kyonke unhon-ne ( hadis mein mazkoor ( ye dua teen ya char sahaba se riwayat ki ya jaisey unhon-ne kaha, (yani jitney sahaba se unhon-ne kaha, ("
1334,"Waleed ne Auzai se, unhon-ne abu Ammar . unka naam Shaddad bin-Abdullah hai. se, unhon-ne abu Asma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab apni Namaz se farigh hotey to teen baar istighfar kartey aur uske baad kehtey : ( اللہم انت السلام و منك السلام ، تباركت ذاالجلال والاكرام) aey Allah ! tu hi salam hai aur salamati teri hi taraf se hai, to bulandi aur barkat wala hai, aey jalaal waley aur izzat bakhshney waley! Waleed ne kaha : maine Auzai se puchha : istighfar kaisey kya jaaey? unhon-ne kaha : ( استغفر اللہ ، استغفر اللہ) kahey."
1335,"Abu-Bakar bin abi-Shabih aur ibne-Numair ne hadis bayan ki, kaha hamein abu-Muawiya ne Aasim se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) salam pherney ke baad sirf ye zikr padhney tak hi ( qibla rukh ( baithtey : (اللہم ! انت السلام ومنک السلام تبارکت ذاالجلال والاکرام) aey Allah! tu hi salam hai aur salamati teri hi taraf se hai, to bulandi w barkat wala hai, aey jalaal waley aur izzat bakhshney waley ! ibne-Numair ki riwayat mein : (یا ذالجلال والاکرام) (ya ke izaafey ke saath) hai"
1336,"abu-Khalid Ahmar ne Aasim se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki aur (یا ذالجلال والاکرام) (ya ke izaafey ke saath) kaha,"
1337,"Shoba ne Aasim aur Khalid se riwayat kartey huey Abdullah-bin-Haaris se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, magar wo ( Shoba (ya (ke izaafey ke saath) (یا ذالجلال والاکرام) kaha kartey they."
1338,"Mansoor ne musaiyeb bin Raafe se, unhon-ne Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Warraad se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne (unke mutaalbey par) Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko likh kar bheja ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se farigh ho kar salam phertey to farmatey : aik Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo Yakta hai, iska koi Sharik nahi, hukumat aur farmanrawai usi ki hai, wahi shukr w sataaish ka haqdaar hai aur har cheez par qudrat rakhney wala hai. aey Allah ! jo kuchh to kisi ko dey usey koi rok sakney wala nahi aur jis cheez ko to rok ley koi usey de sakney wala nahi aur terey samney kisi shaan waley ko uski shaan koi fayda nahi de sakti ."
1339,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Kuraib aur Ahmed bin Sanan ne hamein hadis bayan ki, un sab ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Musaiyab bin Raafe se, unhon-ne Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Warraad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat bayan ki Abu-Bakar aur abu-Kuraib ne apni riwayat mein : ( Warraad ne) kaha : Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye baat mujhey likhwai aur maine ye baat Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf likh bheji ."
1340,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Abda bin abi Lubaba ne khabar di ke Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Warraad ne kaha : Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha . jabke ye tahreer un ( Mughira ( ki khaatir Warraad ne likhi. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, jab wo salam phertey to kehtey. padhi. ( aagey aisey hi hai) jaisey un donon ( Mansoor aur Aamash ( ki hadis hai, siwaey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qaul ( وَھُوَ عَلیٰ کُلِّ شَئیٍ قَدِیٌر (ke , unhon (ibne-Juraij ( ne ye alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
1341,"Ibne-Aun ne abu-Saeed se, unhon-ne Warraad se. jo Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke kaatib they. riwayat ki, kaha : Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf likha ( masla malum kya ( . padhi.  ( aagey ( Mansoor aur Aamash ki hadis ke mutabiq ( hai.)"
1342,"Sufiyan ne kaha : hamein Abda bin abi Lubaba aur abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke kaatib Warraad se suna, wo kehtey they : Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ko khat likha ke mujhey koi aisi cheez likh bhejein jo aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni ho, to unhon-ne likh bheja ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, jab aap Namaz khatm kar letey to farmatey : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له ، له الملك وله الحمد ، وهو علي كل شيء قدير ، اللهم لا مانع لما أعطيت wla معطي لما منعت wla ينفع ذالجد منك الجد) Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, wo akelaa aur Yakta hai, iska koi Sharik nahi, hukumat aur farmanrawai usi ki hai, wahi shukr w sataish ka haqdaar hai aur wahi har cheez par qudrat rakhney wala hai. aey Allah ! jo kuchh to kisi ko dena chahey usey koi rok sakney wala nahi aur terey samney kisi shaan waley ko uski shaan koi fayda nahi de sakti ."
1343,"Muhammad ke walid Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne abu-Zubair se hadis sunai, kaha : ( Abdullah (bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) salam pher kar har Namaz ke baad ye kalimaat kehtey they : aik Allah ke siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi, iska koi Sharik nahi, hukumat aur farmanrawai usi ki hai aur wahi shukr w sataaish ka haqdaar hai aur wahi har cheez par qaadir hai. gunahon se bachney ki taufeeq aur neki karne ki quwwat Allah hi se ( miltii ( hai, iske siwa koi Ilaah w maabood nahi. ham iske siwa kisi ki bandagi nahi kartey, har tarah ki nemat aur Sara Fazal w karam usi ka hai, khoobsurat tareef ka sazawaar bhi wahi hai, Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, ham uske liye Deen mein ikhlas rakhney waley hain, chahey kaafir usko ( kitna hi ( naa pasand karein aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har Namaz ke baad buland awaz se 'la Ilaah illallah' waley ye kalimaat kaha kartey they."
1344,Abda bin Sulaiman ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se aur unhon-ne apne khandan ke Maula abu-Zubair se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) har Namaz ke baad buland awaz se padhtey they ( aagey ( ibne-Numair ki riwayat ki tarah hai aur unhon-ne apni hadis ke aakhir mein kaha : phir ibne-Zubair kehtey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har Namaz ke baad un ( kalimaat ( ko buland awaz se kehtey they.
1345,"Hisham ke bajaey) Hajjaj-bin abi Usman ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujh se abu-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo us member par khutba de rahe they aur keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ya namazon ke aakhir mein salam pherney ke baad kaha kartey they.  .) aagey ( Hisham-bin-Urwa ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
1346,"Musa-bin-Aqba se riwayat hai ke abu-Zubair Makki ne unhein hadis sunai ke unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, jab wo Namaz ke baad salam phertey to kehtey. padhi. ( Baqiya riwayat) un donon ( Hisham aur Hajjaj ( ki) uper zikr ki gaee ( riwayat ki tarah hai, aur aakhir mein kaha : wo usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya kartey they"
1347,"Aasim bin nazar Taimi ne kaha : hamein Moatamir ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne hadis sunai neez (eik aur sanad se) Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne kaha : hamein Leis ne ibne- Ajlan se hadis sunai, un donon (Ubaidullah aur ibne- Ajlan) ne Sumaiie se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. ye Quteba ki riwayat ki hui hadis hai. ke kuchh tangdast muhajir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur guzarish ki : buland darjey aur daaimii nemat to zyada maal waley log le gaey ! aap ne puchha : wo kaisey? unhon-ne kaha : wo isi tarah namazein padhtey hain jis tarah ham padhtey hain, wo isi tarah rozey rakhtey hain jaisey ham rakhtey hain aur wo sadqa kartey hain jabke ham sadqa nahi kar saktey, wo (bandhey houno aur ghulaamon ko) aazad kartey hain jabke ham aazad nahi kar saktey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya to kya phir main tumhen aisi cheez na sikhaaun jis se tum un logon ko paalo gey jo tum se sabqat le gaey hain aur uske zariey se unse bhi sabqat ley jaogey jo tum se baad (aaney waale) hain? aur tum se wahi afzal hoga jo tumhari tarah amal karega. unhon-ne kaha : kyon nahi aey Allah ke rasool ! (zaroor bataein). aap ne farmaya : tum har Namaz ke baad tentis (33) martaba tasbeeh, takbeer aur tahmeed (Subhan-Allah, Allahu-akbar, aur al-hamdulillah) ka wird kya karo abu- Saleh ne kaha : fuqaraaey muhajireen dobara Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huey aur kehney lagey : hamarey maaldaar bhaiyon ne bhi jo ham kartey hain iske barey mein sun liya hai aur isi tarah amal karna shuru kar diya hai (wo bhi tasbeeh, takbeer aur tahmeed karne lagey hain). to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye Allah ka Fazal hai jisey chahey inayat farma de. Quteba ke ilawa Leis se ibne- Ajlan ke hawale se doosrey riwayat karne walon ne ye izafa kya ke Sumaiie ne kaha : maine ye hadis apne ghar ke aik fard ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : tumhen وہم hua hai, unhon (Abu-Saleh) ne to kaha tha : tentis martaba (Subhan-Allah) kaho , tentis baar (al-hamdulillah) kaho aur tentis baar (Allahu-akbar) kaho. main dobara Abu-Saleh ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unhein ye bataya to unhon-ne mera hath pakad kar kaha : ( Allahu-akbar , Subhan-Allah (aur ( al-hamdulillah , Allahu-akbar , Subhan-Allah (aur ( al-hamdulillah ( (is tarah kaho) ke sab ki tadaad tentis ho jaey. ibne- Ajlan ne kaha : maine ye hadis -Rijaa bin Hewa ko sunai to unhon-ne mujhey Abu-Saleh ke waastey se Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (riwaayat kartey huey) usi ki manind (tarah) hadis sunai."
1348,"Umayya-Bistam-Aishi ne mujhey hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Yazeed bin Zaree ne hadis sunai, kaha hamein Rooh ne Suhel se hadis sunai unhon-ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh se) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! buland maraatib aur daaimii ne'matein to zyada maal waley log ley gaey. jis tarah Leis se Quteba ki bayan ki hui hadis hai, magar unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis mein Abu-Saleh ka ye qaul dakhil kar diya hai ke phir fuqaraa muhajireen lot kar aaey, hadis ke aakhir tak aur hadis mein is baat ka izafa kya : Suhel kehtey they : (har kalima ( gyara (11) gyara baar aur ye sab mila kar tentis baar. (ye Suhel ka apna faham (samajh) tha.)"
1349,"Maalik-bin-Mighwal ne hamein khabar di, kaha : maine Hakam-bin-Utaiba se suna, wo Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Lela se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Hazrat Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : (namaz ke ya) aik doosrey ke peechhey kahey janey waley aisey kalimaat hain ke har farz Namaz ke baad unhein kehney wala.  ya unko ada karne wala. kabhi naa-muraad w naakaam nahi rehta, tentis baar ( Subhan-Allah ( , tentis baar ( al-hamdulillah (aur chauntis baar ( Allahu-akbar ( ."
1350,"Hamza Zayyat ne hamein hukm se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se, unhon-ne Hazrat Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : aik doosrey ke baad kahey janey waley ( kuchh ( kalimaat hain, unko kehney wala. ya ada karne wala. nakaam ya namuraad nahi rehta. har ( farz ( Namaz ke baad tentis baar ( Subhan-Allah ( , tentis martaba ( al-hamdulillah (aur chauntis baar ( Allahu-akbar ( kehna ."
1351,Amr bin Qais Mulai ne Hakam se isi sanad ke sath usi ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki.
1352,"Khalid-bin-Abdullaah ne hamein Suhel se khabar di, unhon-ne abu Ubaid Mazhiji se riwayat ki. Imam Muslim (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : abu Ubaid Sulaiman-bin Abdul-Malik ke Maula they. unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yazeed Lesi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki : jisne har Namaz ke baad tentis martaba ( Subhan-Allah ( tentis baar ( al-hamdulillah (aur tentis baar ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha, ye ninyaanwe ho gaey aur so pura karne ke liye (لا الہ الا اللہ وحدہ لا شریک لہ ، لہ Mulk ولہ الحمد ، وہو Ali کل شیء قدیر) kaha iske gunah maaf kar diye jaeinge , chahey wo samandar ke jhaag ke barabar hun."
1353,"Ismail-bin-Zakariya ne Suhel se, unhon-ne abu-Ubaid se, unhon-ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aagey ( uper zikr ki gaee riwayat ( ki tarah riwayat ki."
1354,"Jarir ne Ammara-bin-Qaqa se, unhon-ne Abu-Zaraa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ( shuruat ( Namaz ke liye takbeer kehtey to qirat karne se pahley kuchh der sukoot farmatey, maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan ! dekhiye ye jo takbeer aur qirat ke darmyan aap ki khamoshi hai (iske doran mein) aap kya kehtey hain? aap ne farmaya : main kehta hun : (اللہم باعدبینی وبین خطایای کما باعدت بین المشرق والمغرب اللہم نقنی من خطایای کما ینقی الثوب الابیض من الدنس ، اللہم اغسلنی من خطایای بالثلج والماء والبرد) aey Allah ! mere aur mere gunahon ke darmyan is tarah doori daal de jis tarah tu ney mashriq aur maghrib ke darmyan doori dali hai. aey Allah ! mujhey mere gunahon se is tarah paak saaf kar de jis tarah safaid kapda mail kuchail se saaf kya jata hai. aey Allah ! mujhey mere gunahon se paak kar de barf ke sath , pani ke sath aur olon ke sath."
1355,"ibne- Fuzel aur abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad donon ne, Ammara-bin-Qaqa se, isi sanad ke sath , Jarir ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
1356,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab dusri rakaat se uthtey to ( الحمد اللہ رب العٰلمین) se qirat ka shuruat kar detey ( kuchh der ( khamoshi ikhtiyar na farmatey.
1357,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik aadmi aaya aur saf mein Sharik hua jabke uski saans chadhi hui thi, usne kaha : الحمد للہ حمدا کثیرا طیبا مبارکا فیہ tamam hamd Allah hi ke liye hai, hamd bahut zyada , paak aur barkat wali hamd . jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz poori kar li to aap ne puchha tum mein se ye kalimaat kehney wala kon tha? sab logon ne hont band rakhey . aap ne dobara puchha tum mein ye kalimaat kehney wala kon tha? us ne koi mamnooa baat nahi kahi. tab aik shakhs ne kaha : main is haalat mein aaya ke meri saans phooli hui thi to maine is aalim mein ye kalimaat kahey . aap ne farmaya : maine baara farishton ko dekha jo (is mein) aik doosrey se sabqat ley janey ki koshish kar rahe they ke kon usey uper ley jata hai."
1358,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : aik baar ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padh rahe they ke logon mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : ( اللہ اکبر کبیرا ، والحمد للہ کثیرا ، وسبحان اللہ بکرۃ واصیلا ) Allah sabse bada hai bahut bada , aur tamam tareef Allah ke liye hai bahut zyada aur tasbeeh Allah hi ke liye hai, subah w Sham . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : falan-falan kalima kehney wala kon hai? logon mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! mein hon aap ne farmaya mujhey un par bahut hairat hui, unke liye aasman ke darwazey khol diye gaey. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine jab se aap se ye baat suni , iske baad se un kalimaat ko kabhi tark nahi kya."
1359,"mukhtalif sanadon se Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna jab Namaz khadi ho jaey to uske liye daudtey huey na aao, ( balke is tarah) chaltey huey aao ke tum par sukoon taari ho. (namaz ka ( jo hissey paalo usey padh lo aur jo reh jaey usey pura kar lo."
1360,"( Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma ke bajaey) Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Namaz ki takbeer keh di jaey to tum uske liye bhaagtey huey mat aao, is tarah aao ke tum par sukoon ho, (namaz ka ( jitna hissey paalo, padh lo aur jo reh jaey usey pura kar lo kyonke jab koi shakhs Namaz ka irada karke aata hai to wo Namaz ( hi ( mein hota hai."
1361,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( sun kar) hamein sunain, unhon-ne bahut si hadisein zikr kin, unmein se ye bhi thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Namaz ke liye bulaawaa diya jaey to uske liye chaltey huey aao, aur tum par sukoon (taari) ho, jo (namaz ka hissa ( mil jaey, wo padh lo aur jo reh jaey usey mukammal kar lo."
1362,"Muhammad-bin-Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Namaz ke liye iqamat keh di jaey to tum mein se koi shakhs uski taraf bhag kar na aaey balke is tarah chal kar aaey ke is par sukoon aur waqaar taarii ho, jitni (namaz ( pa lo, padh lo aur jo tumharey ( pahunchne ( se pahley guzar chuki usey pura kar lo."
1363,"Muawiya bin Salam ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se riwayat ki kaha : Abdullah-bin-abi-Qatada ne mujhey khabar di ke unke walid ne unhein bataya , kaha : ham (eik baar ( jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padh rahe they, to aap ne ( jaldi chalney , daud kar pahunchne ki) mili-juli awazein sunin, aap ne (namaz ke baad) puchha : tumhen kya hua (tha?) logon ne jawab diya ham ne Namaz ke liye jaldi ki. aap ne farmaya : aisey na kya karo, jab tum Namaz ke liye aao to sukoon w itminan malhooz rakho, (namaz ka hissa ( jo tumhen mil jaey, padh lo aur jo guzar jaey usey pura kar lo."
1364,(Muaawiya ke bajaey) Sheban ne ( Yahya se) isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki.
1365,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim aur Ubaidullah bin Saeed ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Hajjaj sawaaf se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne abu-Salma aur Abdullah-bin-abi-Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Namaz ke liye iqamat kahi jaey to us waqt tak khadey na hua karo jab tak mujhey na dekh lo aur ibne- Hatim ne kaha : jab iqamat kahi jaey ya ( jamat ke liye) pukara jaey."
1366,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Mamar se hadis sunai, Abu-Bakar (bin abi-Shabih ne mazeed ( kaha : hamein ibne-Ulaih ne Hajjaj-bin-abi-Usman se hadis sunai, neez Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Esa-bin-Yonus aur Abdur-Razzaq ne Mamar se khabar di. Ishaq ne ( mazeed ( kaha : hamein Waleed bin Muslim ne Sheban se khabar di, un sab (Mamar, Hajjaj-bin abi Usman aur Sheban ( ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-abi-Qatada se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. Ishaq ne Mamar aur Sheban se jo hadis riwayat ki usmein ye izafa kya hai. yahan tak ke tum mujhey dekh lo ke main bahar nikal aaya hun."
1367,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they, ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein) iqamat kahi gaee, ham apni taraf Rasulullah ke aaney se pahley hi khadey ho gaey aur apne musalley par khadey ho gaey aap ne Allahu-akbar nahi kaha tha ke aapko ( kuchh ( yad aa gaya, is par aap wapas palat gaey aur hamein farmaya : apni jagah par raho. ham aap ke intizar mein khadey rahe yahan tak ke aap tashrif ley aaey, aap ghusl kiye huey they aur aap ke sar se pani ke qatrey tapak rahe they, phir aap ne ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha aur hamein Namaz padhai."
1368,"Zuhair-bin-Harab ne bayan kya ke hamein Waleed-bin-Muslim ne hadis sunai, (kaha) : hamein abu-Amr , yani Auzai ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Zohri ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey hadis sunai kaha : Namaz ki iqamat keh di gaee, logon ne apni safain baandh leen aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif la kar apni jagah par khadey ho gaey phir aap ne logon ko hath ke ishaarey se farmaya : apni jagah par raho aur khud (masjid se) bahar nikal gaey, phir ( aaey to (aap ghusl farma chukey they aur aap ke sar se pani tapak raha tha, phir aap ne unhein Namaz padhai."
1369,"Ibrahim-bin-Musa ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha hamein Waleed-bin-Muslim ne baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye iqamat kahi jati to us se pahley ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (apni jagah par) khadey hon, log safon main apni apni jagah ley letey."
1370,"Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne farmaya, jab suraj dhal jata to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Zohar ki azan kehtey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nikalney tak takbeer na kehtey. jab aap hujrey se nikaltey to aapko dekh kar iqamat kehtey."
1371,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam-Malik ke samney ibne-Shahab Zohri se riwayat ki hui hadis padhi unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne Namaz ki aik rakaat pa li , yaqinan us ne Namaz pa li ."
1372,"(Imam Malik ke bajaey) Yunus ne ibne-Shahab Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne imam ke sath Namaz ki aik rakaat pa li , us ne Namaz pa li ."
1373,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Mamar, Auzai, Yunus aur Ubaidullah sab ne Zohri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Yahya ki Imam Malik se uper zikr ki gaee riwayat ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur unmein se kisi ki hadis main imam ke saath ke alfaz nahi hain. aur Ubaidullah ki hadis mein hai : to yaqinan us ne mukammal Namaz pa li."
1374,"Imam Malik ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se riwayat ki, unhein Ata-bin-Yasar, Basar-bin-Saeed aur Aaraj ne hadis bayan ki, un sab ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne suraj nikalney se pahley subah ki aik rakaat pa li to yaqinan us ne subah (ki Namaz ( pa li aur jisne suraj ke ghurub honey se pahley Asr ki aik rakaat pa li to yaqinan us ne Asr (ki Namaz ( pa li ."
1375,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah riwayat ki jis tarah Imam Malik ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se riwayat ki."
1376,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne suraj ke ghurub honey se pahley Asr ki Namaz ka aik sajda pa liya ya suraj ke nikalney se pahley subah ki Namaz ka to yaqinan us ne us Namaz ko pa liya. ( ibne-Shahab ne kaha ( sajdey se murad rakaat hi hai."
1377,"Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne Mamar se, unhon-ne ibne- Taaus se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat ( Abdullah (bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne suraj ke ghurub honey se pahley Asr ki Namaz mein se aik rakaat pa li to yaqinan us ne (namaz ( pa li aur jisne suraj nikalney se pahley fajr ki aik rakaat pa li to yaqinan us ne (namaz ( pa li ."
1378,Moatamir ne kaha : maine Mamar se suna. padhi.  aagey isi sanad se (riwaayat ki).
1379,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke aik din Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez ne Asr ki Namaz mein kuchh taakheer kar di to Urwa ne unse kaha : baat yun hai ke Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ‌ nazil huey aur imam bin kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz padhai. to umr (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne unse kaha : aey Urwa ! jaan lein ( samajh lein) aap kya keh rahe hain ! unhon-ne kaha : maine Basheer-bin-abii- Masood se suna, wo kehtey they : maine abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : Jibreel utrey aur unhon-ne (namaz mein) meri imamat ki, maine unke sath Namaz padhi, phir maine unke sath Namaz padhi, phir unke sath Namaz padhi, phir unke sath Namaz padhi, phir unke sath Namaz padhi. wo apni ungliyon se panch namazein shumaar kartey they."
1380,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab Zohri se riwayat ki ke aik din Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ne Namaz mein taakheer kar di to Urwa-bin-Zubair unke paas aaey aur unhein bataya ke mugheer-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik din Namaz der se padhi us waqt wo Kufa mein they abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas aaey aur kaha : Mughira ! ye kya hai? kya aapko pata nahi ke Jibreel ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ utrey they, unhon-ne Namaz padhai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unke saath) Namaz padhi, phir unhon-ne Namaz padhi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi, phir unhon-ne Namaz padhi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unke saath) Namaz padhi, phir unhon-ne Namaz padhi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unke saath) Namaz padhi, phir ( Jibreel ne) kaha : mujhey iska hukm diya gaya hai. to umr ne Urwa se kaha : Urwa ! dekh lo, kya keh rahe ho? kya Jibreel ne khud (aa kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye (har ( Namaz ka waqt mutaiyan kya tha? to Urwa ne kaha Basheer-bin-abii- Masood apne walid se aisey hi bayan kartey they."
1381,"Zohri se Imam Malik ki pichhli sanad hi se riwayat hai ke Urwa ne kaha : mujhey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu-anha) Mina ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz (us waqt) padhtey ke dhoop unke hujrey mein hoti, ( hujrey mein se) dhoop bahar nikalney se pahley. (maghribii diwar ka saaya hujrey ke darwazey tak na pahuncha hota.)"
1382,"Abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Shabih aur Amr-Naaqid ne hadis sunai, Amr ne kaha : Sufiyan ne hamein Zohri se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz padhtey they aur suraj mere hujrey mein chamak raha hota tha, abhi ( sehan ke mashriqii hissey mein) saaya na phaila hota tha Abu-Bakar ne ( mana ke wazaahat kartey huey) kaha : abhi ( mashriq ki taraf ( saaya zahir na hua hota tha."
1383,"Yunus ibne-Shahab ne riwayat ki, kaha mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne bataya ke mujhey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz us waqt padhtey they jabke dhoop unke hujrey mein hoti ( mashriq ki taraf phailtaa ( saaya unke hujrey mein na phaila hota."
1384,Hisham ne apne walid Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz padhtey aur dhoop mere hujrey mein pad rahi hoti thi
1385,"Muaz bin Hisham ne hamein apne walid se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne abu-Ayub se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum fajr ki Namaz padho to suraj ka pahlaa kinara namudaar honey tak iska waqt hai, phir jab tum Zohar padho to Asr honey tak iska waqt hai aur jab tum Asr padho to suraj ke zard honey tak iska waqt hai aur jab tum maghrib padho to shafaq ( surkhi (ke khatm honey tak iska waqt hai aur jab tum isha padho to aadhi raat honey tak iska waqt hai."
1386,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se, unhon-ne abu-Ayub se hadis sunai. abu-Ayub ka naam Yahya-bin-Malik-azdii hai. unko ( muraaghii ( bhi kaha jata hai aur) muraagh ( qabila azdahii ki aik shaakh hai. unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Zohar ka waqt tab tak hai jab tak Asr ka waqt shuru na ho, aur Asr ka waqt hai jab tak suraj zard na ho, aur maghrib ka waqt hai jab tak shafaq ghurub na ho, aur isha ka waqt aadhi raat tak hai aur fajr ka waqt hai jab tak suraj tuloo na ho."
1387,"abu-Aamir aqadii aur Yahya-bin-abi-Bukair ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki. un donon ki riwayat mein, Shoba ne kaha : unhon ( Qatada ( ne aik baar us hadis ko marfoo bayan kya aur do baar marfoo bayan nahi kya. ( marfoo wo hai jiski sanad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchey.)"
1388,"Hammam ne hamein hadis bayan ki (kaha ( : hamein Qatada ne abu-Ayub se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Zohar ka waqt ( shuru hota hai) jab suraj dhal jaey aur aadmi ka saaya uske qad ke barabar ho ( janey tak) , jab tak Asr ka waqt nahi ho jata ( rehta hai) aur Asr ka waqt (hai) jab tak suraj zard na ho jaey aur maghrib (مغر ب) ka waqt ( hai) jab tak surkhi ghayab na ho jaey aur isha ki Namaz ka waqt raat ke pahley nisf tak hai aur subah ki Namaz ka waqt poou phtney  se us waqt tak ( hai) jab tak suraj tuloo nahi hota, jab suraj tuloo honey lagey to Namaz se ruk jao kyonke wo shaitan ke do seengon ke darmyan nikalta hai."
1389,"Hajjaj ne jo Hajjaj Aslami ke betey hain, Qatada se, unhon-ne abu Ayub se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se namazon ke oqaat ke barey mein puchha gaya to aap ne farmaya : fajr ki Namaz ka waqt us waqt tak hai jab tak suraj ka pahlaa kinara na nikley, aur Zohar ka waqt hai jab suraj aasman ki darmyan se maghrib ki taraf dhal jaey yahan tak ke Asr ka waqt ho jaey aur Asr ki Namaz ka waqt hai jab tak suraj zard na ho jaey aur iska ( ghurub honey wala ( pahlaa kinara doobney lagey, aur maghrib ki Namaz ka waqt tab hai jab suraj ghurub ho jaey jo surkhi ghayab honey tak rehta hai aur isha ki Namaz ka waqt aadhi raat tak hai."
1390,Abdullah-bin-Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne kaha : maine apne walid ko ye kehtey suna : ilm jism ki raahat se hasil nahi ho sakta.
1391,"saiyedna Barida (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik shakhs ne Namaz ka waqt puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum 2 roz hamarey sath Namaz padho '' . phir jab aaftaab dhal gaya saiyedna Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya, unhon-ne azan di, phir hukm diya, unhon-ne iqamat kahi , phir Asr padhi aur suraj buland tha safaid saaf phir hukm diya to iqamat kahi maghrib ki jab aaftaab doob gaya, phir hukm diya to iqamat kahi isha ki jab shafaq doob gaee, phir hukm diya iqamat kahi fajr ki jab fajr tuloo hui, phir jab doosra din hua, hukm kya to Zohar thandey waqt padhi aur bahut thandey waqt padhi aur Asr padhi aur suraj buland tha magar roz awwal se zara taakheer ki aur maghrib padhi shafaq doobney se pahley aur isha padhai tehai raat ke baad aur fajr padhi jab khub roshni ho gaee. phir farmaya : ''wo saail kahan hai jo Namaz ka waqt poochhta tha? '' usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! mein hazir hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye jo donon waqt tum ne dekhey unke beech mein tumhari Namaz ka waqt hai.''"
1392,"Harmi bin Umara ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Alqama bin-Marsad se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Barida se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se namazon ke oqaat ke barey mein sawal kya aap ne farmaya namazon mein hamarey sath maujood raho. phir aap ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhon-ne andherey mein azan kahi , jab fajr tuloo hui aap ne subah ki Namaz padhai , phir jab suraj aasman ke darmyan se dhala to aap ne unhein Zohar ka hukm diya, phir jab suraj ( abhi ( uncha tha, aap ne unhein Asr ka hukm diya, phir jab suraj ghurub ho gaya to aap ne unhein maghrib ka hukm diya, phir jab shafaq nichey chali gaee to unhon-ne subah ko roshan honey diya ( phir fajr ada ki) , phir unhein Zohar ka hukm diya to unhon-ne usey thanda honey diya, phir unhein Asr ka hukm diya jabke suraj abhi safaid aur saaf tha, usmein zardi ki koi aamezish (milawat) na thi, phir unhein shafaq gir ( kar ghayab ho ( janey se qabl maghrib ke barey mein hukm diya, phir tehai raat ya raat ka kuchh hissey guzar janey ke baad unhein isha ke barey mein hukm diya. Harmi ko shak hua. phir jab subah hui to aap ne poochha. saail kahan hai? jo tum ne dekha, unke darmyan ( namazon ka ( waqt hai."
1393,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne hamein hadis sunai (kaha : ( mere walid ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein badr bin Usman ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Abu-Bakar bin abi Musa ne apne walid se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ke paas aik saail namazon ke oqaat poochhney ke liye hazir hua to aap ne usey ( zabani ( kuchh jawab na diya. kaha : jab fajr ki po phooti to aap ne fajr ki Namaz padhai jabke log ( andherey ki wjah se) aik doosrey ko pehchan nahi pa rahe they, phir jab suraj dhala to aap ne unhein ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko) hukm diya aur unhon-ne Zohar ki iqamat kahi jabke suraj abhi buland tha, phir jab suraj nichey chala gaya to aap ne unhein hukm diya to unhon-ne maghrib ki iqamat kahi, phir jab shafaq ghayab hui to aap ne unhein hukm diya to unhon-ne isha ki iqamat kahi, phir agley din fajr mein taakheer ki, yahan tak ke us waqt se farigh huey jab kehney wala kahey, suraj nikal aaya hai ya nikalney ko hai, phir Zohar ko muakhkhar kya yahan tak ke guzishta kal ki Asr ke qareeb ka waqt ho gaya, phir Asr ko muakhkhar kya ke jab salam phera to kehney wala kahey : aaftaab mein surkhi aa gaee hai, phir maghrib ko muakhkhar kya yahan tak ke shafaq ghurub honey ke qareeb hui, phir isha ko muakhkhar kya yahan tak ke raat ki pehli tehai ho gaee phir subah hui to aap ne saail ko bulwaya aur farmaya : (namaz ka ( waqt un donon ( waqton (ke darmyan hai."
1394,"Wakee ne badr bin Usman se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Abu-Bakar bin abi Musa se sun kar ye hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke aik saail Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir hua aur aap se namazon ke oqaat ke barey mein sawal kya. padhi. ( aagey ( ibne-Numair ki riwayat ki tarah hai, siwaey iske ke unhon-ne kaha : doosrey din aap ne maghrib ki Namaz shafaq ghayab honey se pahley padhi."
1395,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne ( Saeed (bin Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab garmi shadeed ho jaey to Namaz thandey waqt mein padho kyonke garmi ki shiddat dozakh ki lapton (garmi ke phailaao) mein se hai."
1396,"Yunus ne bataya , unhein ibne-Shahab ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bataya ke un donon ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. bilkul isi tarah ( jaisey pichhli hadis mein hai.)"
1397,"Amr (bin Haris bin Yaqoob Ansari ( ne khabar di ke Bukair (bin-Abdullah makhzumi ( ne unhein Basar-bin-Saeed aur Sulaiman Agharr se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab garm din ho to Namaz thandey waqt main ( padho ( kyonke garmi ki shiddat dozakh ki lapton mein se hai. Amr ne kaha : aur mujhey abu Yunus ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Namaz ko thandey waqt tak muakhkhar karo kyonke garmi ki sakhti jahannam ki garmi ke phailaao (lapton) mein se hai. Amr ne kaha : mujhey ibne-Shahab ne bhi) Saeed (bin Musaiyab aur abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey isi tarah hadis sunai jis tarah uper hai."
1398,"Alaa ne apne walid ( Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye garmi aatishe-dozakh ki lapton mein se hai, isliye Namaz thandey waqt mein padho ."
1399,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye wo hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se (eik ( ye hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : namazon mein garmi se bchney ke liye ( waqt) thanda honey do kyonke garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki lapton mein se hai."
1400,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka muazzan Zohar ki azan deney laga to aap ne farmaya : ( waqt ko) thanda honey do, thanda honey do. ya farmaya : intizar karo, intizar karo aur farmaya : bila shubah garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki lapton mein se hai, isliye jab garmi shadeed ho jaey to Namaz thandey waqt tak muakhkhar karo. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul hai : (namaz mein itni taakheer ki gai) yahan tak ke ham ne teelon ka saaya dekha."
1401,"ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, kaha : mujh se abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aag ne apne rab ke huzoor shikayat ki aur kaha : aey mere rab! mera aik hissey doosrey ko kha raha hai. to Allah ne usey 2 saans leney ki ijazat ata kar di : aik saans sardi main aur aik saans garmi mein, garmi aur sardi ke mausam mein jo tum shadeed tareen garmi aur shadeed tareen sardi mehsus kartey ho to ye wahi ( cheez ( hai."
1402,Aswad bin Sufiyan ke aazad karda ghulam Abdullah-bin Yazeed ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman bin Soban se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab garmi ho to Namaz thandey waqt tak muakhkhar karke padho kyonke garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki lapat se hoti hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye bhi zikr farmaya : ( jahannam ki) aag ne apne rab ke huzoor shikayat ki to Allah ne usey saal mein 2 saans leney ki ijazat di : aik saans sardi main aur aik saans garmi mein.
1403,"Muhammad-bin Ibrahim ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : aag ne kaha : aey mere rab! mera aik hissey doosrey ko kha raha hai, mujhey saans leney ki ijazat marahmat farmaa. to ( Allah ne) usey 2 saans leney ki ijazat di : aik saans sardi main aur aik saans garmi mein. tum jo sardi ya thandak ki shiddat patey ho, wo jahannam ki saans se hai aur jo tum haraarat ya garmi ki shiddat patey ho to wo ( bhi) jahannam ki saans se hai."
1404,Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz us waqt padhtey they jab suraj dhalta tha.
1405,"abu-Ahwas Salaam-bin Saleem ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abu-Ishaq se, unhon-ne Saeed bin Wahab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Khabbaab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shadeed garm ret par Namaz ada karne ki shikayat ki to aap ne hamari shikayat ka izaala na farmaya."
1406,"Zuhair ne kaha : hamein Abu-Ishaq ne Saeed bin Wahab se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat Khabbab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se ret ki garmi ki shikayat ki to aap ne hamari shikayat ka izala na farmaya, Zuhair ne kaha : maine Abu-Ishaq se puchha : kya Zohar ke barey mein) shikayat ki? ( unhon-ne jawab diya : haan. maine kaha : kya usko jaldi padhney (ki mashaqqat) ke barey mein? unhon-ne jawab diya : haan."
1407,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham garmi ki shiddat main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey they, jab ham mein se koi apni peshani zamin par na rakh sakta to apna kapda phaila kar is par sajda kar leta ."
1408,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne kaha : Leis ne hamein ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne unko bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz ( aisey waqt mein) padhtey they jab suraj buland aur zinda ( roshni mein kami ke baghair ( hota tha, Awali ki taraf janey wala (asr padh kar) chalta aur Awali (Madina ke oopri hissey ki bastiyon mein) pahunchta to suraj abhi buland hota tha. ye bastiyan Madina se 2 se 8 mail ki masafat par thin. Quteba ne (apni hadis mein) Awali pahunchne ka zikr nahi kya."
1409,"Amr ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz padhtey they. ( aagey ( bilkul ( uper ki riwayat (ke mutabiq hai."
1410,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke ham Asr ki Namaz padhtey they, phir janey wala Quba jata, un logon ke paas pahunchta aur suraj abhi uncha hota. (Qubaa Madina se 2 mail ki masafat par hai.)"
1411,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke, kaha ham Asr ki Namaz padhtey, phir aik insan banu-Amr-bin-Auf ke mahalley (Quba mein) jata to unhein Asr ki Namaz padhtey huey paata."
1412,"Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat hai ke wo namaze-Zohar se farigh ho kar Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan Basra mein unke ghar hazir huey, unka ghar masjid ke pahlu mein tha, jab ham unki khidmat mein pahunchey to unhon-ne puchha : kya tum logon ne Asr ki Namaz padh li hai? ham ne unse kaha : ham to abhi Zohar ki Namaz padh kar lautey hain. unhon-ne farmaya : to Asr padh lo. ham ne uth kar (asr ki) Namaz padh li, jab ham farigh huey to unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna ye munafiq ki Namaz hai, wo betha hua suraj ko dekhta rehta hai yahan tak ke (jab wo zard pad kar) shaitan ke 2 seengon ke darmyan chala jata hai to khada ho kar us (namaz ( ki char thongein mar deta hai aur is mein Allah ko bahut hi kam yad karta hai."
1413,"Hazrat abu Amama bin Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : ham ne Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez (Rehmatullahi-alaih) Mina ke sath Zohar ki Namaz padhi, phir ham bahar nikley aur Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to ham ne unhein Asr ki Namaz padhtey huey paya , maine puchha : chacha jaan ! ye kon si Namaz hai jo aap ne padhi hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : Asr ki hai, aur yahi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz hai jo ham aap ke sath padha kartey they."
1414,"Amr bin suwaad Aamiri , Muhammad-bin Salma Muradi aur Ahmed bin Esa ne hamein hadis bayan ki. un sab ke alfaz miltey-jultey hain. Amr ne kaha : hamein khabar di aur baqi donon ne kaha : hamein hadis sunai ibne- Wahab ne, kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Haris ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se khabar di ke Musa bin Sad Ansari ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hafs bin Ubaidullah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Asr ki Namaz padhai to jab aap farigh huey, aap ke paas banu-Salma ka aik aadmi aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! ham apna oont nehar karne ka irada rakhtey hain. aur ham chahtey hain aap bhi us mauqe par maujood hun. aap ne farmaya : achchha. aap nikal padey, ham bhi aap ke sath chal padey, ham ne dekha, oont abhi zabah nahi kya gaya tha, usey zabah kya gaya, phir iska gosht kaataa gaya, phir usmein se kuchh pakaya gaya, phir ham ne suraj ghurub honey se pahley (usey) kha liya. Muradi ka qaul hai ke hamein ye hadis ibne- Wahab ne ibne-Lahiya aur Amr-bin-Haris donon se riwayat kartey huey sunai."
1415,"hamein Waleed bin Muslim ne hadis sunai, kaha : Auzai ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu Najashi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath namaze-Asr padhtey , phir oont zabah kya jata, iske das hissey kiye jatey, phir ham usey pakaatey aur suraj ke ghurub honey se pahley ham achi tarah pakka hua gosht kha letey."
1416,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Esa-bin-Yonus aur Shuaib bin Ishaq dimashqi ne khabar di, un donon ne kaha : hamein Auzai ne isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon ( Ishaq ( ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein Asr ke baad oont zabah kartey they, ye nahi kaha : ham aap ke sath Namaz padhtey they."
1417,Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ki namaze-Asr reh gaee to maano iske ahal w ayaal aur iska maal tabah w barbad ho gaey.
1418,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Amr Naqid ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne apne walid ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se hadis bayan ki. Amr ne kaha : ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) us hadis ki sanad ko) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak) pahunchaatey they Abu-Bakar ne kaha : ( unhon-ne (us hadis ko marfooan bayan kya."
1419,"Amr-bin-Haris ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ki Asr ki Namaz reh gaee to maano iske ahal w ayaal aur uska maal tabah w barbad ho gaey."
1420,"abu-Usama ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hisham se, unhon-ne Muhammad se unhon-ne Ubeda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-Ehzaab ke din farmaya : Allah Taala un ( mushrekeen ( ki qabron aur gharon ko aag se bhar de, jis tarah unhon-ne hamein darmyani Namaz (asr ( se rokaa aur) jang mein) mashghool kiye rakha yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho gaya."
1421,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne aur Motamir bin Sulaiman ne Hisham se ye hadis ( baqi bachi ( isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki.
1422,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Qatada se suna, wo abu Hassan se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Ubeda se aur unhon Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-Ehzaab ke din farmaya : un logon ne hamein darmyani Namaz se mashghool kiye rakha yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho gaya, Allah Taala unki qabron ko aur gharon ko ya ( farmaya : ( unke peton ko aag se bhar de. gharon ya peton ke barey mein Shoba ko shak hua."
1423,"Saeed ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki aur unhon-ne baghair shak ke ""unke gharon aur qabron ko"" kaha."
1424,"Yahyaa-bin-Jazaar ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-Ehzaab ke mauqe par jab aap khandaq ki guzar gaahon mein se kisi guzar gaah par tashrif farma they, farmaya : unhon-ne hamein darmyani Namaz (asr ( se mashghool kar diya yahan tak ke suraj doob gaya, Allah Taala unki qabron aur gharon ko ya farmaya : unki qabron aur peton ko aag se bhar de."
1425,"Shutair bin shakl ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehzaab ke din farmaya : unhon-ne hamein darmyani Namaz (yani ( Asr ki Namaz se mashghool rakha, Allah Taala unke gharon aur qabron ko aag se bhar de. phir aap ne usey raat ki donon namazon maghrib aur isha ke darmyan padha. ( maghrib ka waqt ja raha tha isliye aakhiri waqt mein pahley maghrib padhi, phir Asr ki qaza padhi, phir isha padhi.)"
1426,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mushrikon ne (jang mein mashghool rakh kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Asr ki Namaz se rokey rakha yahan tak ke suraj surkh ya zard ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unhon-ne hamein darmyani Namaz , Asr ki Namaz se mashghool rakha , Allah Taala unke peton aur qabron mein aag bhar de. ya farmaya : Allah Taala unke peton aur qabron ko aag se bhar de. ( ملأ ( ki jagah ( حشا (ka lafz irshad farmaya, mafhoom donon ka aik hi hai.)"
1427,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam abu Yunus se riwayat hai, kaha Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey hukm diya ke unke liye Quran Majeed likhun farmaya : jab tum us aayat par pahuncho (حفظو Ali الصلوت والصلوۃ الوسطی) to mujhey batana chunanche jab main aayat par pahuncha to unhein aagah kya, unhon-ne mujhey likhwaayaa : (حافظوا Ali الصلوت والصلاۃ الوسطی وصلاۃ العصر ، قوموا اللہ قانتین) namazon ki hifazat karo aur) khas kar) darmyani Namaz ki, yani namaze-Asr ki aur Allah ke huzoor aajizana qiyam karo. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : maine usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisey hi suna."
1428,"Fuzel bin marzooq ne Shaqiq bin Aqba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke ye aayat (isi tarah) (حافظوا Ali الصلوٰت وصلاۃ العصر) nazil hui, jab tak Allah Taala ko manzoor hua ham ne usey padha, phir Allah Taala ne usey mansukh kar diya aur aayat is tarah utri : (حفظوا Ali الصلوٰت والصلوٰۃ الوسطیٰ) namazon ki nigehdasht karo aur (khususan) darmyan ki Namaz ki is par aik aadmi ne, jo Shaqiq ke paas betha hua tha, unse kaha : to phir us se murad Asr ki Namaz hui? Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main tumhen bata chuka hun ke ye aayat kaisey utri aur Allah Taala ne kaisey usey mansukh kya, ( asl haqiqat ( Allah hi behtar janta hai"
1429,"Aswad-bin-Qais ne Shaqeeq-bin-Aqba se, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham ye aayat aik waqt tak Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (usi tarah) padhtey rahe. padhi. ( aagey ( Fuzail-bin-marzooq ki (pichhli) hadis ki manind (tarah) hai."
1430,"Muaz-bin-Hisham ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein mere walid ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey hadis bayan ki ke khandaq ke roz Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) kuffaare-Quraish ko bura bhala kehney lagey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! Allah ki qism ! main Asr ki Namaz nahi padh saka tha yahan tak ke suraj ghurub honey ko aa gaya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! maine ( bhi) nahi padhi. phir ham ( wadi ( Bathaan mein utrey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur ham ne bhi wuzu kya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suraj ke ghurub ho janey ke baad Asr ki Namaz padhi, phir iske baad maghrib ki Namaz ada ki."
1431,Ali bin-Mubarak ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath usi ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki.
1432,"abu Zinad ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : raat ke Farishtey aur din ke Farishtey aik doosrey ke peechhey tumharey darmyan aatey hain aur fajr ki Namaz aur Asr ki Namaz ke waqt wo ikatthey ho jatey hain, phir jinhoney tumharey darmyan raat guzari hoti hai wo uper chaley jatey hain, unse unka rab poochhta hai, halanke wo unse zyada janta hai : tum mere bandon ko kis haal mein chhod kar aaey ho? wo jawab detey hain : ham unhein (is haalat mein) chhod kar aaey hain ke wo Namaz padh rahe they aur ham unke paas ( kal Asr ke waqt) us haalat mein pahunchey they ke wo Namaz padh rahe they."
1433,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : Farishtey aik doosrey ke peechhey tumharey paas aatey hain. (is hadis mein malaaika ka lafz ( یتعاقبون ( se pahley hai.) . padhi. ( baqi riwayat ( abu Zinad ki riwayat ki tarah hai"
1434,"Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Marwan bin Muawiya fazari ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Ismail bin abi Khalid ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Qais-bin abi Hazim ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jareer-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kahey rahe they : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they ke aap ne chaudahwin raat ke chaand ki taraf nazar ki aur farmaya : suno ! tum log apne rab ko is tarah dekhogey , jis tarah us poorey chaand ko dekh rahe ho, iske dekhney main tum bheed na lagaao gey , agar tum ye kar sako ke suraj nikalney se pahley ki aur suraj ghurub honey se pahley ki Namaz main ( masroofiyat , sustii wghaira se) maghloob na ho (to tumhen ye nemat uzmaa mil jaey gaee. (aap ki murad Asr aur fajr ki Namaz se thi, phir Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ne ye aayat padhi (وسبح بحمد ربک قبل طلوع الشمس وقبل غروبہا) aur apne rab ki hamd ki tasbeeh bayan karo, suraj ke nikalney se pahley aur uske ghurub honey se pahley ."
1435,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne Abdullah-bin-Numair , abu-Usama aur Wakee se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, usmein hai : suno ! tum log yaqinan apne rab ke samney pesh kiye jaogey aur usko isi tarah dekhogey , jis tarah us por ے chaand ko dekhtey ho. phir munasib ne ( ثم قراء جریر) ke bajaey) ( ثم قراء) ( phir unhon-ne padha ( kaha aur Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam nahi liya."
1436,"(Ismail ( ibne-abi-Khalid , Misar aur bakhtri bin Mukhtar ne ye riwayat Abu-Bakar bin Umara bin Rubiya se suni , unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat Umara bin Rubiya Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : wo shakhs hargiz aag mein dakhil nahi hoga jo suraj nikalney aur uske ghurub honey se pahley Namaz padhta hai. yani fajr aur Asr ki namazein. is par Basra ke aik aadmi ne unse kaha : kya aap ne ye riwayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi? unhon-ne kaha : haan. us aadmi ne kaha : main shahadat deta hun ke maine bhi ye riwayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni. mere donon kanon ne usey suna aur mere dil ne usey yad rakha."
1437,"abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ne Hazrat Umara bin Rubiya ke betey se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo insan suraj nikalney aur uske ghurub honey se pahley Namaz padhta hai wo aag mein dakhil nahi hoga aur unke paas Basra ka aik baashinda bhi maujood tha, us ne puchha : kya aap ne ye hadis seedhey-seedhey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni? to unhon-ne kaha : haan, aur main uski shahadat deta hun. us aadmi ne kaha : aur main bhi shahadat deta hun ke maine usi jagah unko ye farmatey huey suna jahan aap ne unse suna tha."
1438,"Haddab bin Khalid azdii ne kaha : hamein Hammam bin Yahya ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey abu jamara Zubai ne Abu-Bakar (bin abi Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne 2 thandey waqton ki namazein ada kin, wo jannat mein dakhil hoga. ( din ka thanda waqt Asr ka aur raat ka sabse thanda waqt fajr ka hota hai.)"
1439,Bishr bin Sari aur Amr bin Aasim donon ne kaha : ham se Hammam ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Abu-Bakar ka nasb bayan kya aur kaha : ibne-abi-Musa.
1440,Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maghrib ki Namaz us waqt padhtey jab suraj ghurub hota aur pardey ki ot mein chala jata.
1441,"Waleed bin Muslim ne kaha : ham se Auzai ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham se abu Najashi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maghrib ki Namaz padhtey to ham mein se koi shakhs laut-ta aur wo apne teer ke girney ki jaghein dekh sakta tha."
1442,"Shuaib bin Ishaq Dimashqi ne Auzai se pichhli sanad ke sath Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham maghrib ki Namaz ada kartey. padhi. ( aagey ( pichhli hadis ki tarah hai."
1443,"Amr-bin-Sawwad Aamiri aur Harmala-bin-Yahya donon ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Yunus ne khabar di ke unhein ibne-Shahab ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha ki Namaz khub andhera honey tak muakhkhar farmai aur usi Namaz ko utma ( gehri taareeki ke waqt ki Namaz ( kaha jata tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (us waqt tak) ghar se na nikley yahan tak ke Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (masjid mein aaney wali) auratein aur bachchey so gaey hain. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur nikal kar masjid ke haaziriin se farmaya : ahale-zameen mein se tumharey siwa is Namaz ka aur koi bhi intizar nahi kar raha aur ye logon mein (Madina se bahar ( Islam phailney se pahley ki baat hai. Hurmala ne apni riwayat mein izafa kya ke ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey bataya gaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey liye munasib na tha ke tum Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Namaz ke liye israar kartey. ye tab hua jab Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne buland awaz se pukara .) unhon-ne ghaaliban ye samjha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhool gaey hain ya so gaey hain)."
1444,Aqeel ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki lekin usmein Zohri ka qaul : ( وذکرلی ( (mujhey bataya gaya) aur uske baad ka hissa bayan nahi kya.
1445,"Muhammad-bin-Bakr , Hajjaj-bin-Muhammad aur Abdur-Razzaq . sab ke alfaz aapasii miltey-jultey hain. sab ne kaha : ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Mugheera-bin-hakeem ne Umme-Kulsum-bint-abi-Bakr se khabar di ke unhon-ne unhein ( Mughira ko) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey huey khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : aik raat Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha ki Namaz mein der kar di yahan tak ke raat ka bada hissey guzar gaya aur ahal masjid so gaey, phir aap bahar tashrif le gaey, Namaz padhai aur farmaya : agar (mujhey ( ye (dar) na hota ke main apni ummat ko mashaqqat mein daalun ga to yahi iska ( behtreen ( waqt hai. aur Abdur-Razzaq ki hadis mein hai : agar ye (dar) na hota ke ye meri ummat ke liye mashaqqat ka sabab banega ."
1446,"Hakam ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik raat ham isha ki aakhiri Namaz ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka intizar kartey rahe, jab raat ka tehai hissey guzar gaya ya iske ( bhi) baad aap tashrif laaey, hamein malum nahi ke aapko ghar walon (ke mamley ( mein kisi cheez ne mashghool rakha tha ya koi aur baat thi, jab aap bahar aaey to farmaya : bila shubah tum aisi Namaz ka intizar kar rahe ho jiskaa tumharey siwa kisi aur Deen ke pairo kaar intizar nahi kar rahe, aur agar mujhey ye dar na hota ke ye meri ummat ke liye nagawar hoga to main unhein isi ghadi mein (ye) Namaz padhaayaa karta. phir aap ne muazzan ko hukm diya, us ne iqamat kahi aur aap ne Namaz padhai."
1447,"hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : ham se Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke aik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( kisi bana par) is (isha ki namaz) se mashghool ho gaey, aap ne usey muakhkhar (dair) kar diya yahan tak ke ham masjid mein so gaey, phir bedaar huey, phir so gaey, phir bedaar huey, phir aap (ghar se) nikal kar hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya : aaj raat tumharey siwa ahal zamin mein se koi nahi jo Namaz ka intizar kar raha ho."
1448,"Sabit se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mehar (ya anguthi) ke barey mein puchha to (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha ki Namaz aadhi raat tak muakhkhar (dair) ki ya aadhi raat guzarney ko thi, phir aap tashrif laey aur farmaya : bila shubah (doosrey) logon ne Namaz padh li aur so chukey , aur tum ho ke Namaz hi mein ho jab tak Namaz ke intizar mein baithey ho. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya : jaisey main ( ab bhi) aap ki chandi se bani anguthi ki chamak dekh raha hun aur unhon-ne baain hath ki ungli uthatey huey chhoti ungli se ( ishara kya ke anguthi usmein thi)."
1449,"abu-Zaid-Saeed-bin-Rabe ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein quraah-bin-Khalid ne Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne aik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka intizar kya yahan tak ke aadhi raat ke qareeb (ka waqt) ho gaya, phir aap aaey aur Namaz padhai. phir aap ne hamari taraf rukh farmaya, aisa lagta hai ke main ( ab bhi) aap ki anguthi ki chamak dekh raha hun, wo aap ke hath mein thi, chandi ki bani hui thi."
1450,Ubaidullah-bin-abdul-Majeed Hanfi ne quraah se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki aur ye bayan na kya : phir aap ne hamaari taraf rukh farmaya.
1451,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : main aur mere (wo ( sathi . jo mere sath badi kashtii mein) Habsha se wapas ( aaey they. Bat-haan ke nashebii maidan mein utrey huey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina mein they aur har raat unmein se aik jamat baari-baari isha ki Namaz mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hoti thi. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ne kaha ke mujhey aur mere sathiyon ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath yun ittifaq pesh aaya ke aap apne kisi mamley main (itney) mashghool ho gaey ke aap ne Namaz ko muakhkhar kar diya yahan tak ke aadhi raat ho gaee. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur logon ko Namaz padhai. jab aap ne Namaz mukammal kar li to un logon se jo aap ke samney hazir they, farmaya : zara thehro main tumhen bataataa hon aur tum khush ho jao ye tum par Allah Taala ki aik nemat hai ke logon mein is waqt , tumharey siwa , koi bhi Namaz nahi padh raha. ya aap ne farmaya : is waqt tumharey siwa kisi ne Namaz nahi padhi. hamein yad nahi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kon sa jumla kaha tha. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ne bataya : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat sun kar khush-khush wapas aaey."
1452,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein khabar di, kaha : maine Ata se puchha : aap ke nazdeek kon si ghadi zyada pasandida hai ke main usmein isha ki Namaz , jisey log utma kehtey hain, imam ke sath ya infiraadii taur par padhun? unhon-ne jawab diya : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ko ye farmatey huey suna : aik raat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha ki Namaz mein der kar di yahan tak ke log soey , phir bedaar huey, phir soey aur bedaar huey to Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur buland awaz se kaha : Namaz ! Ata ne kaha : Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya : to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nikley, aisa lagta hai ke main ab bhi aapko dekh raha hun, aap ke sar Mubarak se qatra-qatra pani tapak raha tha aur) baalon mein se pani nikalney ke liye) aap ne apna hath sar ke aadhey hissey par rakha hua tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar ye baat na hoti ke meri ummat ke liye mashaqqat hogi to main unhein hukm deta ke wo is Namaz ko isi waqt padha karein. (ibne-Juraij ne) kaha : maine Ata se achi tarah puchha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein kis tarah bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath kis andaz se apne sar par rakha tha? to Ata ne mere samney apni ungliyan kisi qadr kholein , phir apni ungliyon ke kinarey sar ki aik taraf rakhey , phir unko dabaatey huey is tarah unko sar par phera yahan tak ke unka angoothaa kaan ke us kinarey ko chhooney laga jo chehrey ke qareeb hota hai, phir kanpatii aur dadhi ke kinarey ko (chhuwa ( bas is tarah kya na ( dabaaw mein) kami ki na kisi cheez ko pakda (aur nichodaa) maine Ata se puchha : aapko kya bataya gaya ke us raat Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kitni taakheer ki? unhon-ne kaha : mujhey malum nahi. Ata ne kaha : mere nazdeek zyada pasandida yahi hai ke main, imam hon ya akelaa , ye Namaz taakheer se padhun , jis tarah Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us raat padhi thi. agar ye baat tumharey liye infiraadii taur par, ba jamat ki sura mein logon ke liye jab tum unke imam ho, dushwari ka baais ho to usko darmyan waqt mein padho, na jaldi aur na muakhkhar (der) karke."
1453,"abu-Ahwas ne Samak se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke , kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ki dusri Namaz taakheer (der) se padhtey they."
1454,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur abu-Kamil Jahdari ne kaha : hamein abu-Awana ne Samak se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) namazein tumhari tarah (ke oqaat mein) padhtey they, albatta isha muakhkhar karke tumhari Namaz se kuchh der baad padhtey they aur Namaz mein kami (kamii) kartey they. aur abu-Kamil ki riwayat main ( یخف فی الصلاۃ (ke bajaey) ( یخفف (ke alfaz hain. (mafhoom aik hi hai.)"
1455,"Zuhair ne kaha : ham se Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne abu-labeed se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : tumhari Namaz ke naam par tumharey ganwaar log ghalib na aa jayen, khabardaar ! ye isha hai, wo oontniyon ka doodh dohney ki wjah se andhera kar detey hain. (aur andherey (utma)) ki bina par is waqt padhi janey wali Namaz ko (Salat (Durud) العتمہ ), yani andherey ki Namaz kehtey hain.)"
1456,"Wakee' ne Sufiyan se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhari Salat (Durud) isha ke naam par baddoo tum par ghalib na aa jayen kyonke Allah ki kitab mein iska naam isha hai : aur baddoo oontniyon ka doodh dohney mein andhera kar detey hain."
1457,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke momin auratein subah ki Namaz Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padhti thin, phir apni chaadrein odhey huey wapas aatiin aur) andherey ki wjah se) koi unhein pehchan nahi sakta tha."
1458,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : kuchh momin auratein fajr ki Namaz main apni chaadrein odhey huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sharik hoti thin, phir wo apne gharon ko laut'tiin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke andherey mein Namaz padhney ki bina par wo pahchaanii na ja sakti thin."
1459,"Nasar-bin-Ali jahazmii aur Ishaq-bin-Musa Ansari ne kaha : hamein Ma'n (معن) ne Malik se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Umra se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : aisa tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz padhtey to auratein apni chaadrein odhey huey gharon ko laut'tiin , (aur ( andherey ki wjah se pahchaanii nahi jati thin. Ansari ki riwayat main (( mutalfiaat (ke bajaey) ( mutlaffifaat ( (chaadaron mein liptii hui) ke alfaz hain."
1460,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ghandar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Sad-bin-Ibrahim se aur unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Hasan-bin-Ali (bin abii-Taalib ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Hajjaj Madina Munawra aaya (aur taakheer se namazein padhney laga ( to ham ne (namaz ke oqaat ke barey mein) Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, unhon-ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz do-pahar ko) zawaal ke fauran baad) padhtey they aur Asr aisey waqt mein padhtey they ke suraj bilkul saaf (aur roshan hota ( tha aur maghrib ki Namaz suraj ghurub hotey hi padhtey aur isha ki Namaz ko kabhi muakhkhar kartey aur kabhi jaldi ada kartey, jab aap dekhtey ke log jama ho gaey hain to jaldi padh letey aur jab unhein dekhtey ke der kar di hai to taakheer kar detey aur subah (ki Namaz ( ye log. padhi. ya kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andherey mein padhtey they."
1461,Muaz Anbari ne Shoba se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Hajjaj namazon mein taakheer kar deta tha to ham ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha. padhi. (aagey) ghandar ki riwayat ki tarah hai.
1462,"Khalid-bin Haris ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : Shoba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey sayyaar-bin-Sulaamaa ne khabar di, kaha : maine suna ke mere walid , Hazrat abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ke barey mein poochh rahe they. (Shoba ne) kaha : maine puchha : kya aap ne khud unhein sunaa? unhon-ne kaha : (isi tarah) jaisey mein abhi tumhen sun raha hun, kaha : maine suna, mere walid unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ke barey mein sawal kar rahe they, unhon-ne bataya ke aap us, yani isha ki Namaz ko kuchh (taqriban) aadhi raat tak muakhkhar karne mein muzaayqa (haraj) na samajhtey they aur us Namaz se pahley soney aur uske baad baat cheet karne ko naa pasand farmatey they. Shoba ne kaha : main baad azan ( dobara ( unse mila to maine unse ( phir ( puchha to unhon ( Sayyar ( ne kaha : aap Zohar ki Namaz suraj dhalney ke waqt padhtey they aur Asr aisey waqt mein padhtey ke insan Namaz padh kar Madina ke door tareen hissey tak pahunch jata aur suraj (usi tarah) zinda ( roshan aur garm ( hota tha aur unhon-ne kaha : maghrib ke liye mein nahi janta, unhon-ne kon sa waqt bataya tha. ( Shoba ne) kaha : main iske baad (phir) Sayyar se mila aur unse puchha to unhon-ne bataya : (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) subah ki Namaz aisey waqt mein padhtey ke insan salam phertaa aur apne sath baithey huey insan ke chehrey ko , jisey wo janta hota, dekhta to usey pehchan leta aur aap us (namaz ( mein sath se so tak aayatein tilawat farmatey they."
1463,"Muaz Anbari ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne sayyaar-bin-Sulaamaa se riwayat ki ke maine abu-Barza ko kehtey huey suna, Rasulullah isha ki Namaz mein kuchh (yani ( aadhi raat tak taakheer ki parwaana kartey they aur us se pahley soney aur uske baad guftgu karne ko pasand nahi farmatey they. Shoba ne kaha : phir main unhein dobara mila to unhon-ne kaha : ya tehai raat tak."
1464,"(Shoba ke bajaey) Hammaad-bin-Salma ne abu Minhal ( Sayyar bin Sulaamaa ( se riwayat ki, kaha : maine abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isha ko tehai raat tak muakhkhar kar detey they aur us se pahley soney aur baad mein guftgu karne ko na-pasand farmatey they aur subah ki Namaz mein sou se lekar sath tak aayatein tilawat farmatey aur aisey waqt mein salam phertey they jab ham aik doosrey ke chehrey ko pehchan saktey they."
1465,"Khalaf-bin-Hisham, abu-Rabeea' Zahrani aur abu-Kamil Jahdari ne hadis bayan ki, kaha hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Imran Jawni se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Samit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : tumhara kya haal hoga jab tum par aisey log hukmaraan hongey jo Namaz ko iske waqt se muakhkhar karengey ya Namaz ko iske waqt se khatm kar dengey ? maine kaha to aap mujhey (iske barey mein) kya hukm detey hain? aap ne farmaya : tum apne waqt par Namaz padh lena agar tumhen unke sath ( bhi) Namaz mil jaey to padh lena , wo tumharey liye nafl ho jaeygi. Khalaf ne ( an (an) وقتھا ( (iske waqt se) ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
1466,"Jafar-bin-Sulaiman ne abu-Imran Jawni se isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se kaha : Abu-Zar ! mere baad aisey hukmaraan aaeingey jo Namaz ko mar dengey ( unka waqt khatm kar dengey ( to tum Namaz ko iske waqt par padh lena , agar tum ne Namaz waqt par padh li to (unke sath ada ki gaee dusri Namaz ( tumharey liye nafl ho jaeygi warna tum ne apni Namaz to bacha hi li hai."
1467,"Shoba ne abu-Imran se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : mere khaleel ne mujhey hukm diya tha ke main sunoon aur farmaanbardaarii karun chahey katey huey baazuon wala ghulam (hi hukmaraan) ho aur ye ke main Namaz waqt par padhun (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( phir agar tum logon ko us haalat mein paogey ke unhon-ne Namaz padh li hai to tum apni Namaz bacha chukey ho ( waqt par pahley padh chukey ho) , aur agar (unhon-ne nahi padhi aur tum unke sath Sharik huey) to tumhari ye Namaz nafl hogi."
1468,"Budail se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu Aaliya se suna, wo Abdullah-bin-Samit se aur wo Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kar rahe they, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur meri raan par hath maara : tumhara kya haal hoga jab tum aisey logon main apni Baqiiya zindagi guzaar rahe hogey jo Namaz ko iske waqt se muakhkhar kar dengey ? ( Abdullah-bin-Samit ne) kaha : unhon-ne kaha : aap kya hukm detey hain? farmaya : tum Namaz ko iske waqt par ada kar lena , aur apni zarurat ke liye chaley jana , phir agar Namaz ki iqamat kahi gaee aur tum masjid mein huey to (dobara) padh lenaa."
1469,"Ayub ne abu-Aaliya-barra'a se riwayat ki, kaha : ibne- Ziyad ne Namaz mein taakheer kar di to mere paas Abdullah-bin Samit tashrif ley aaey, maine unke liye kursi rakhwaa di, wo is par baith gaey, maine unke samney ibne- Ziyad ki harkat ka tazkira kya to is par unhon-ne apna ( nichlaa ( hont daanton mein dabaayaa aur meri raan par hath mar kar kaha : jis tarah tum ne mujh se puchha hai, isi tarah maine Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha tha, unhon-ne bhi isi tarah meri raan par hath maara tha jis tarah maine tumhari raan par hath maara hai aur kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha tha jis tarah tum ne mujh se puchha hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri raan par hath maara jis tarah maine tumhari raan par hath maara hai aur farmaya : tum Namaz bar-waqt ada kar lena , phir agar tumhen unke sath Namaz padhni padey to ( phir se) Namaz padh lena aur ye na kehna : maine Namaz padh li hai is liye ab nahi padhunga ."
1470,"abu N-aama ne Abdullah-bin Samit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum logon ka kya haal hoga ya farmaya : tumhari kaifiyat kya hogi jab tum aisey logon mein reh jaogey jo Namaz ko iske waqt se muakhkhar karengey ? tum waqt par Namaz padh lena , phir agar ( tumhari maujoodgi mein) Namaz ki iqamat ho to tum unke sath ( bhi) padh lena kyonke ye neki mein izafa hai."
1471,"Matar ne abu Aaliya Barra se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Abdullah-bin Samit se puchha ke ham Juma ke din hukmaraanon ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhtey hain aur wo Namaz ko muakhkhar kar detey hain. to unhon-ne zor se meri raan par hath maara jis se mujhey takleef mehsus hui aur kaha : maine iske barey mein Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne ( bhi) meri raan par hath maara tha aur kaha tha : maine iske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya tha to aap ne farmaya : Namaz iske waqt par ada kar lo, phir un ( hukmaraanon (ke sath apni Namaz ko nafl bana lo. kaha : Abdullah ne kaha : mujhey bataya gaya ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( bhi) Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ki raan par hath maara tha."
1472,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ba-jamaat Namaz tumharey akeley ki Namaz se pachchis guna afzal hai."
1473,"Abdul-Aala ne Mamar se, unhon-ne Zohri se, isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : sab ke sath mil kar Namaz padhna akeley insan ki Namaz se pachchis darjey afzal hai. aap ne farmaya : raat ke Farishtey aur din ke Farishtey fajr ki Namaz mein jama hotey hain. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum chaho to ye aayat padh lo (jo is baat ki tasdeeq karti hai) : aur fajr ke waqt Quran padhna bila shubah fajr ki qirat mein haziri di jati hai."
1474,"Shuaib ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Saeed aur abu-Salma ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they.  aagey Mamar se Abdul-Aala ki) uper zikr ki gaee ( hadis ki tarah hai, iske siwa ke unhon-ne ( darjey ki bajaey) pachchis Juz kaha."
1475,"Salman Agharr ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : baa-jamaat Namaz akeley ki pachchis namazon ke barabar hai."
1476,"Umar-bin Ata-bin abi khuwaar ne khabar di ke main Naafe bin Juber bin Mut-im ke paas betha hua tha ke is beech mein hamarey paas se johniyon ke aazad karda ghulam Zaid-bin zaban ke behnoi abu Abdullah guzrey , Naafe ne unhein bulaya (aur hadis sunaney ko kaha, ( unhon-ne kaha : maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : imam ke sath ( padhi gai) Namaz aisi pachchis namazon se afzal hai jo insan akeley padhta hai."
1477,Malik ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ba-jamat Namaz padhna akeley ki Namaz se sattais darjey afzal hai.
1478,"Yahya ne Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : aadmi ki jamat ke sath Namaz uski akeley padhi gaee sattais namazon se badh kar hai."
1479,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : hamein abu-Usama aur) Muhammad-bin-Abdullah ( ibne-Numair ne hadis sunai, neez ibne-Numair ne (kaha : ( hamein mere walid ne hadis sunai, un donon ( abu-Usama aur ibne-Numair ( ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki. ibne-Numair ne apne walid se riwayat ki hui hadis main bees se ziyada ke alfaz riwayat kiye aur Abu-Bakar bin abi-Shabih ne apni riwayat mein sattais darjey kaha,"
1480,"Suhak ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, farmaya : bees se zayed ."
1481,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ko aik Namaz mein ghair hazir paya to farmaya : maine ( yahan tak) sochaa ke kisi aadmi ko logon ki imamat karaaney ka hukm dun, phir dusri taraf se un logon ki taraf jaun jo Namaz se peechhey rahtey hain aur unke barey mein (apne kaarindon ko) hukm dun ke lakdiyon ke gathon se aag bhadka kar unke gharon ko un par jalaa dein. unmein se agar kisi ko yaqin ho ke Namaz mein haziri se usey farba ( gosht se bhari hui) haddi milegi to wo usmein zaroor hazir ho jaeyga Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad isha ki Namaz se thi."
1482,"Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : munaafiqon ke liye sabse bhari Namaz isha aur fajr ki Namaz hai, agar un logon ko pata chal jaey, jo unmein ( khair w barkat ( hai to chahey unhein ghutnon ke bal chal kar aana padey, zaroor aaein aur maine sochaa tha ke Namaz ki iqamat ka hukm dun, phir kisi shakhs ko kahun wo logon ko jamat kiraaey , phir main kuchh ashkhaas ko sath lekar, jinke paas lakdiyon ke gatthey hon, un logon ki taraf jaun jo Namaz mein hazir nahi hotey , phir unke gharon ko un par aag se jalaa dun."
1483,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah se riwayat kin, phir unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein se ye bhi thi ke Rasulullah ne farmaya : maine irada kya tha ke apne jawaanon ko hukm dun ke wo meri khaatir lakdi ke gatthey tayaar karein, phir kisi aadmi ko hukm dun wo logon ko Namaz padhaaey , phir gharon ko unke (be Namaz ( baasiyon samet jalaa diya jaey."
1484,Yazeed bin Asamm ne Abu-Hurera (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis riwayat ki hai.
1485,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un logon se jo Jumey se peechhey reh jatey hain, farmaya : maine irada kya ke kisi aadmi ko hukm dun wo logon ko Namaz padhaaey , phir un logon ke gharon ko un par (is samet ( jalaa dun jo Jumey se peechhey rahtey hain."
1486,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik naa-beena aadmi hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! mere paas koi laney wala nahi jo ( hath se pakad kar) mujhey masjid mein ley aaey. us ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darkhaast ki ke usey ijazat di jaey ke wo apne ghar mein Namaz padh ley. aap ne usey ijazat de di, jab wo wapas hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey bulaya aur farmaya : kya tum Namaz ka bulaawa ( azan ( suntey ho? usne kaha : ji haan. aap ne farmaya : to is par labbaik kaho."
1487,"abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ne abu-Ahwas se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : sathiyon samet maine khud ko dekha ke Namaz se koi shakhs peechhey na rehta, siwaey munafiq ke , jiska nifaq malum hota ya siwaey bimar ke aur) kabhi-kabhi) bimar bhi 2 aadmiyon ke sahaarey se chalta aa jata yahan tak ke Namaz mein shamil ho jata. unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hidayat ke tariqon ki taleem di aur hidayat ke tariqon mein se aisi masjid mein Namaz padhna bhi hai jis mein azan di jati ho."
1488,"Ali-bin Aqmar ne abu-Ahwas se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : jo ye chahey ke kal (qiyamat ke din) Allah Taala se musalman ki haisiyat se miley to wo jahan se un ( namazon (ke liye bulaya jaey, un namazon ki hifazat karey ( wahan masaajid mein ja kar sahi tarah se unhein ada karey) kyonke Allah Taala ne tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ley hidayat ke tareeqey muqarrar farma diye hain aur ye ( masaajid mein ba-jamaat namazein ( bhi unhi tariqon mein se hain. kyonke agar tum namazein apne gharon mein padhogey, jaisey ye jamat se peechhey rehney waalaa, apne ghar mein padhta hai to tum apne Nabi ki raah chhod doge aur agar tum apne Nabi ki raah ko chhod doge to gumrah ho jaogey . koi aadmi jo pakeezgi hasil karta hai) wuzu karta hai) aur achi tarah wuzu karta hai, phir un masaajid mein se kisi masjid ka rukh karta hai to Allah Taala iske har qadam ke badley, jo wo uthata hai, aik neki likhta hai, aur uske sabab iska aik darja buland farmata hai aur iska aik gunah kam kar deta hai, aur maine dekha ke ham mein se koi ( bhi) jamat se peechhey na rehta tha, siwaey aisey munafiq ke jiska nifaq sab ko malum hota ( balke kabhi-kabhi aisa hota ke) aik aadmi ko is tarah laya jata ke usey 2 aadmiyon ke darmyan sahara diya gaya hota, yahan tak ke saf mein la khada kya jata."
1489,"Ibrahim bin muhajir ne abu-Shasa se riwayat ki, kaha : ham masjid mein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath baithey huey they ke muazzan ne azan kahi , aik aadmi masjid se uth kar chal padaa , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne musalsal is par nazar rakhi yahan tak ke wo masjid se nikal gaya, Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye shakhs , yaqinan us ne abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nafarmani ki hai."
1490,"Ashas bin abi Shasa Maharibi ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna : unhon-ne aik shakhs ko azan ke baad masjid mein se chal kar bahar nikaltey dekha to farmaya : ye shakhs , bila shubah us ne abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nafarmani ki hai."
1491,"abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : ham se Usman bin-Hakim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman bin abi Umra ne hadis sunai, kaha : Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) maghrib ki Namaz ke baad masjid mein tashrif laey aur akeley baith gaey, main bhi unke paas baith gaya, wo kehney lagey : bhatijey ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jisne isha ki Namaz ba-jamaat ada ki to maano us ne aadhi raat ka qiyam kya aur jisne subah ki Namaz ( bhi) jamat ke sath padhi to maano us ne saari raat Namaz padhi."
1492,Sufiyan ne abu Sehal Usman bin-Hakim se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki.
1493,"Bishr , yani ibne- Mufazzal ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne Khalid se aur unhon-ne Anas bin Sirin se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Jundub bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne subah ki Namaz padhi wo Allah Taala ki zimme-dari ( aman ( mein hai. to aisa na ho ke) aisey shakhs ko kisi tarah nuqsan pahunchaney ki bina par) Allah Taala tum (main se kisi shakhs) se apne zimmey ke barey mein kisi cheez ka mutalba karey, phir wo usey pakad ley , phir usey aundhey munh jahannam mein daal de."
1494,"Ismail ne Khalid se aur unhon-ne Anas bin Sirin se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Jundub ( bin-Abdullah ) qasri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne subah ki Namaz ada ki, wo Allah ke zimmey mein aa gaya, ( dua hai) Allah tum se apne zimmey ke hawale se koi mutalba na karey kyonke jis se wo apne zimmey mein se kisi cheez ka mutalba kar ley , usey pa leta hai, phir usey aundhey munh jahannam ki aag mein daal deta hai."
1495,yahi riwayat Hasan Basri ne Jundub bin Sufiyan ke hawale se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki) lekin aakhiri fiqra ( (فیکبہ فی نار جہنم) ( usko jahannam mein aundhey munh phenk deta hai) bayan nahi kya.
1496,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke Mehmood-bin Rabe Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse bayan kya ke Hazrat Utban bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawan sahaba kiram mein se they jo Ansar mein se jange-badr mein Sharik huey they, ( bayan kya (ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! meri nazar kharaab ho gaee hai, main apni qaum ko Namaz padhaata hun aur jab baarishein hoti hain to mere aur unke darmyan wali wadi mein sailaab aa jata hai, uski wjah se main unki masjid mein nahi pahunch sakta ke main unhein Namaz padhaaun to aey Allah ke rasool! mein chahta hun ke aap ( mere ghar ( tashrif laaein aur Namaz padhney ki kisi aik jagah par Namaz padhein taake main us jagah ko (mustaqil taur par) jaey Namaz bana loon. kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : insha-Allah main aisa karunga . Utban (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to subah ke waqt din chadhtey hi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (andar aaney ki) ijazat talab farmai, maine tashrif aawrii ka kaha, aap aa kar baithey nahi yahan tak ke ghar ke andar (ke hissey mein) dakhil huey, phir puchha : tum apne ghar mein kis jagah chahtey ho ke main ( wahan ( Namaz padhun ? maine ghar ke aik koney ki taraf ishara kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey ho kar takbeer ( tahreema ( kahi aur ham aap ke peechhey khadey ho gaey, aap ne 2 rakatein ada farmaein , phir salam pher diya. iske baad ham ne aapko khizeer ( gosht ke chhotey tukdon se baney huey khaney (ke liye rok liya jo ham ne aap ke liye taiyaar kya tha. ( Utban (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : (aap ki aamad ka sun kar) ird-gird se mahalley ke log aagey yahan tak ke ghar mein khasi tadaad mein log ikatthey ho gaey. unmein se aik baat karne waley ne kaha : Malik bin Dukhshun kahan hai? unmein se kisi ne kaha : wo to munafiq hai, Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat nahi rakhta. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : iske barey mein aisa na kaho , kya tumhen malum nahi ke usne Allah ki raza hasil karne ke liye ( لا الہ الا اللہ ( kaha hai? ( Utban (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to logon ne kaha : Allah aur uskey rasool hi zyada jaanney waley hain. us (ilzam lagaaney waale) ne kaha : ham to uski tawajjoh aur uski khair-khahi munaafiqon hi ke liye dekhtey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak Allah Taala ne aisey shakhs ko aag par haram qarar diya hai jo ( لا الہ الا اللہ ( kehta hai aur uske zariey se Allah ki raza ka talabgar hai. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : maine ( baad mein) Husain bin-Muhammad Ansari se, jo banu- Salim se talluq rakhtey hain unke sardaaron mein se hain, Mehmood-bin Rabe (Raziallahu anhu) ki us hadis ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne usmein un ( Mehmood (Raziallahu anhu)) ki tasdeeq ki."
1497,"Mamar ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Mehmood-bin Rabe (Raziallahu anhu) ne Utban bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir hua. padhi. phir Yunus ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, albatta ye kaha : to aik aadmi ne kaha : Malik bin Dukhshun ya Dukhaishin kahan hai? aur hadis mein ye izafa kya : Mehmood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kahan : maine ye hadis chand logon ko , jin mein abu Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they, sunai to unhon-ne kaha : main nahi samajhta ke jo baat tum bayan kartey ho Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmai ho. is par maine (dil mein) qism khaai ke agar main Utban (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan dobara gaya to unse (iske barey mein zaroor ( poochhunga. to main dobara unke paas aaya, maine dekha ke wo bahut boodhey ho chukey hain, unki beenai khatm ho chuki thi lekin wo ( ab bhi) apni qaum ke imam they. main unke pahlu mein baith gaya aur unse us hadis ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne mujhey bilkul isi tarah ( saari ( hadis sunai jis tarah pahley sunai thi. Zohri ne kaha is waqiey ke baad bahut se faraaiz aur doosrey umur (baton) ( ehkaam ( nazil huey aur hamari nazar mein mamla unhi par tamam hua, lihaza jo insan chahta hai ke) Utban (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ke zahiri mafhoom se) dho ka na khaaey , wo dhoka khaney se bachchey."
1498,"Auzai se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey Zohri ne Hazrat Mehmood-bin Rabe (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka wo kulli karna achi tarah yad hai jo aap ne hamarey ghar mein aik dol se (pani lekar ( ki thi (aur iska pani mere munh par daala tha) . Mehmood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey Utban bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! meri nazar mein kharabi paida ho gaee hai aur is baat tak hadis bayan ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhai aur ye ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (Jasheesha) (khizeer se miltey-jultey khaney (ke liye rok liya jo ham ne aap ke liye banaya tha. unhon ( Auzai ( ne iske baad Yunus aur Mamar wala izafa bayan nahi kya"
1499,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unki naani Muleka (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khaney par bulaya jo unhon-ne taiyaar kya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein se ( kuchh ( khaya, phir farmaya : khadey ho jao mein tumhari ( barkat ki) khaatir Namaz padhun . Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main khada hua aur apni aik chataai ki taraf badha jo lamba arsa istemal honey ki wjah se kali ho chuki thi, maine ( usey saaf karne ke liye) is par pani bahaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par khadey huey, main aur) wahan maujood aik ( yateem bachchey ne aap ke peechhey saf banai , boodhi khatun hamarey peechhey ( khadi (ho gain . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey ( husool barkat ke) liye 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir tashrif ley gaey."
1500,"abu Tayyah ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tamam insanon mein sabse zyada khoobsurat akhlaq ke Malik they. kabhi-kabhi aap hamarey ghar mein hotey aur Namaz ka waqt ho jata, phir aap us chataai ke barey mein hukm detey jo aap ke nichey hoti, usey jhaada jata, phir is par pani chhidka jata, phir aap imamat farmatey aur ham aap ke peechhey khadey hotey aur aap hamein Namaz padhatey . kaha : unki chatai kajhoor ke patton ki hoti thi."
1501,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey yahaan tashrif laey wahan mere, meri walida aur meri khala umme-Haraam ke siwa koi na tha, aap ne farmaya : khadey ho jao main tumhen Namaz padha dun. ( farz ( Namaz ke waqt ke baghair , aap ne hamein Namaz padhai. aik aadmi ne Sabit se puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko apni kis taraf khada kya tha? unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein apne daain hath khada kya tha. phir aap ne hamarey , sab ghar walon ke liye duniya aur aakhirat ki tamam bhalaaiyon ki dua farmai, iske baad meri maan kehney lagi : Allah ke rasool ! (ye) aap ka chhota sa khidmat guzaar hai, Allah se uske liye (khususi) dua karein. kaha : aap ne mere liye har bhalai ki dua ki aur mere liye aap ne jo dua ki iske aakhir mein ye tha, aap ne farmaya : aey Allah ! iska maal aur uski aulad zyada kar aur uske liye unmein barkat daal de."
1502,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abdullah-bin Mukhtar se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Musa-bin-Anas se suna, wo Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aur unki walida ya unki khala ko Namaz padhai , kaha : aap ne mujhey apni daain taraf aur aurat ko hamarey peechhey khada kya."
1503,Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki.
1504,"Abdullaah-bin-Shaddaad se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne hadis bayan ki, farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhtey aur main aap ke samney hoti aur aksar aisa hota ke jab aap sajda kartey to aap ka kapda mujhey lagta aur aap ( khajoor ke patton aur dhaagon se bani hui ( aik jaey-namaz par Namaz padhtey they."
1505,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : hamein Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan hazir huey to dekha ke aap aik chatai par Namaz padh rahe hain, usi par sajda kar rahe hain."
1506,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aadmi ki ba-jamaat ( ada ki gai) Namaz uski ghar mein ya bazar mein padhi hui Namaz ki nisbat bees se zyada darjey badh kar hai aur wo yun ke jab unmein se koi wuzu karta hai aur achi tarah wuzu karta hai, phir masjid aata hai, usey Namaz hi ne uthaya hai aur Namaz ke ilawa kuchh nahi chahta . to wo koi qadam nahi uthata magar iske sabab se iska darja buland kar diya jata hai aur iska aik gunah mitaa diya jata hai, yahan tak ke masjid mein dakhil ho jata hai, phir jab masjid mein dakhil ho jata hai to jab tak Namaz usey rokey rakhti hai wo Namaz hi mein hota hai (iske intizar ka waqt Namaz mein shumaar hota hai) aur tum mein se koi shakhs jab tak us jagah rehta hai jahan us ne Namaz padhi hai to Farishtey iske haq mein dua kartey rahtey hain. wo kehtey hain : aey Allah is par raham farma ! aey Allah ! iski tauba qabool farma ! jab tak wo us jagah ( par kisi ko) takleef nahi pahunchata aur jab tak wo us jagah be-wuzu nahi hota."
1507,"absar, Ismail-bin-Zakariya aur Shoba , sab ne Aamash ki isi sanad ke sath iske ham mana riwayat bayan ki."
1508,"Ibne-Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs jab tak apni (namaz padhney ki) jagah par betha rehta hai, Farishtey iske haq mein dua kartey rahtey hain, kehtey hain : aey Allah ! isey bakhsh de ! aey Allah is par raham farma ! jab tak wo be-wuzu nahi hota, neez jab tak tum mein se kisi shakhs ko Namaz rokey rakhti hai, wo Namaz hi mein hota hai."
1509,abu-Raafe ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : banda musalsal Namaz hi mein hota hai jab tak wo Namaz ki jagah par Namaz ke intizar mein rehta hai aur Farishtey kehtey rahtey hain : aey Allah ! isey maaf farma ! aey Allah ! is par raham farma ! yahan tak ke wo chala jata hai ya be-wuzu ho jata hai. ( abu Raafe kehtey hain : ( maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : ''yuhdis'' ( يحدث (ka matlab kya hai? unhon-ne kaha : awaz ke baghair ya awaz ke sath hawa khaarij kar dena.
1510,"abu-Zinad ne A'araj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tak tum mein se kisi ko Namaz rokey rakhti hai wo musalsal Namaz mein hota hai, usey ghar ki taraf lotney se Namaz ke ilawa aur kisi cheez ne nahi rokaa hota."
1511,ibne-Shahab ne ( Abdur-Rehman (bin Hurmuz ( A'araj ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs jitni der Namaz ke intizar mein baithtaa hai Namaz hi mein rehta hai jab tak be-wuzu na ho jaey. Farishtey uske liye dua kartey rahtey hain : aey Allah ! isey maaf farma ! aey Allah ! is par raham farmaa.
1512,Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ke mutabiq riwayat ki.
1513,"Abdullah-bin-baraad-Ash'arii aur abu-Kuraib donon ne kaha : ham se abu-Usama ne bareed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Barda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Namaz mein sabse zyada sawab uska hai jo uske liye zyada door se chal kar aata hai. phir (iske baad) jo unmein se sabse zyada door se chal kar aata hai. aur jo aadmi Namaz ka intizar karta hai taake usey imam ke sath ada karey, ajr mein us se bahut badh kar hai jo Namaz padhta hai, phir so jata hai. abu-Kuraib ki riwayat mein hai : yahan tak ke wo usey imam ke sath jamat mein ada kare."
1514,"absar ne hamein khabar di, unhon-ne Sulaiman Taimi se, unhon-ne abu-Usman nehdi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Uobai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik aadmi tha, mere ilm mein koi aur aadmi uski nisbat masjid se zyada faasley par nahi rehta tha aur uski koi Namaz nahi chooktii thi, us se kaha gaya - ya maine (us se) kaha : agar aap gadhaa khareed lein ke) raat ki) taareeki (andherey) aur) do-pahar ki) garmi mein aap is par Sawar ho jaya karein. us ne jawab diya : mujhey ye baat pasand nahi hai ke mera ghar masjid ke padaus mein ho, mein chahta hun mera masjid tak chal kar jana aur jab main ghar walon ki taraf lautoon to mera lautnaa mere liye likha jaey. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne ye sab kuchh tumharey liye ikattha kar diya hai."
1515,Moatamir-bin-Sulaiman aur Jarir donon ne Taimi se isi sanad ke sath usi ke mutabiq riwayat ki.
1516,"Ibad-bin-Ibad ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Aasim ne abu-Usmaan se hadis sunai, kaha : Ansar mein aik aadmi tha, iska ghar , Madina mein sabse door) waaqe ( tha aur uski koi Namaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein padhney se chooktii nahi thi, ham ne uske liye hamdardii mehsus ki to maine usey kaha : janab ! agar aap aik gadhaa khareed lein jo aapko garmi aur zamin ke) zahreeley ( keedon se bachaaey (to kitna achchha ho ! ( usne kaha : magar Allah ki qism ! mujhey ye pasand nahi ke mera ghar ( khemey ki tarah) tanaabon ke zariey se Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar se bandhaa hua ho. mujhey uski ye baat bahut nagawar guzri yahan tak ke main usi kaifiyat mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aapko is baat ki khabar di. aap ne usey bulwaya to usne aapko bhi wahi jawab diya aur aapko bataya ke wo aaney-janey par ajr ki ummeed rakhta hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen yaqinan wahi ajr milega jisey tum hasil karna chahtey ho.''"
1517,ibne-Uena aur Wakee ne apne walid ke hawale se Aasim se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki.
1518,"abu-Zubair ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : hamarey ghar masjid se door waaqe they, ham ne chaha ke ham apne gharon ko farokht karke masjid ke qareeb aa jayen to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein rok diya aur farmaya : tumharey liye har qadam ke badley mein aik darja hai."
1519,"Jurairi ne abu-Nazra se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki) masjid ke ird-gird ki jaghein khali huin to (unke qabeeley ( banu- Salma ke logon ne irada kya ke masjid ke qareeb muntaqil ho jayen, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat pahunchi to aap ne unse kaha : mujhey khabar pahunchi hai ke tum masjid ke qareeb muntaqil hona chahtey ho. unhon-ne kaha : ji haan , aey Allah ke rasool! ham yahi chahtey hain. to aap ne farmaya : banu- Salma ! apne gharon mein raho, tumharey qadmon ke nishan likhe jatey hain, ( phir farmaya : ( apne gharon hi mein raho, tumharey qadmon ke nishan likhe jatey hain."
1520,"Kahmas ne abu-Nazra se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : banu- Salma ne masjid ke qareeb muntaqil honey ka irada kya, kaha : aur (masjid ke qareeb ( jaghein ( bhi) khali thin. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye khabar pahunchi to aap ne farmaya : aey banu- Salma ! apne gharon mein raho, tumharey qadmon ke nishan likhe jatey hain. to unhon-ne kaha : (iske baad) hamein ye baat achi (bhi) na lagti ke ham muntaqil ho chukey hotey ."
1521,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne apne ghar mein wuzu kya, phir Allah ke gharon mein se uske kisi ghar ki taraf chal kar gaya taake Allah ke farzon mein se aik fareezey ko ada karey to iske donon qadam (ye kartey hain ke) unmein se aik gunah mitaataa hai aur doosra darja buland karta hai."
1522,"Leis aur Bakr donon ne ibne-Haad se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya - aur Bakr ki riwayat mein hai ke unhon ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya - tum kya samajhtey ho agar tum mein se kisi ke ghar ke samney nehar ho jis se wo har roz panch martaba nahaataa ho, kya us (ke jism (ka koi mail kuchail baqi reh jaeyga ? sahaba ne kaha : uska koi mail kuchail baqi nahi rahega. aap ne farmaya yahi panch namazon ki misal hai, Allah Taala unke zariey se gunahon ko saaf kar deta hai."
1523,"Aamash ne abu-Sufiyan ( Talha-bin-Naafe ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch namazon ki misal tum mein se kisi aik ke darwazey par chaltii hui bahut badi nehar ki si hai, wo usmein se rozaana panch baar ghusl karta ho. (Aamash ne Abu-Sufiyan ke bajaey Hasan ke hawale se riwayat kartey huey) kaha : Hasan ne kaha : ye ghusl iske jism par koi mail kuchail nahi chhodey ga ."
1524,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki : jo shakhs din ke pahley hissey mein ya din ke doosrey hissey mein masjid ki taraf gaya Allah Taala (har baar aaney par) uske liye jannat mein mezbaanii ka intizam farmata hai, jab bhi wo ( aaey ( subah ko aaey ya Sham ko aaey."
1525,"abu-khaisma ne Samak-bin-Harab se riwayat kartey huey khabar di, kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : kya aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath majaalis mein Sharik hotey they? kaha : haan ! bahut . aap jis jagah subah ya din ke shuruati hissey ki Namaz ada farmatey, suraj tuloo honey tak wahan se na uthtey . jab suraj tuloo ho jata to uth khadey hotey , log daure-jaahiliyat mein kiye kaamon ke mutaalliq baatein kartey aur hanstey they aur aap ( bhi unki baatein sun kar) muskuratey they."
1526,"Sufiyan aur Zakariya donon ne Samak se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab fajr padhtey they, to apni Namaz ki jagah par baithey rahtey yahan tak ke suraj achi tarah nikal aataa."
1527,abu-Ahwas aur Shoba donon ne Samak se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki lekin (حسنا) achi tarah (suraj nikal aata) nahi kaha.
1528,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : shehron mein pyari jagah Allah ke nazdeek masjidein hain, aur Allah ke nazdeek ( insani ( aabaadiyon ka sabse na-pasandida hissey unke bazar hain."
1529,"abu-Awana ne hamein Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab (namaz padhney waale) teen hon to unmein se aik unki imamat kiraaey aur unmein se imamat ka zyada haqdaar wo hai jo unmein se zyada (Quran) padha ho."
1530,"Shoba , Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba aur Muaz (bin Hisham) ne apne walid ke waastey se, sab ne Qatada se apney-apney shagirdon ki isi sanad ke sath iske jaisi riwayat bayan ki."
1531,"(Qatada ke bajaey) jureirii ne abu-Nazra se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki."
1532,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Saeed ashajj ne abu-Khalid Ahmar se, unhon-ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ismail-bin -Rijaa se, unhon-ne aos-bin-zamaj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : logon ki imamat wo kiraaey jo unmein se kitabullah ko zyada padhney wala ho, agar padhney mein barabar hon to wo jo unmein se sunnat ka zyada aalim ho, agar wo sunnat (ke ilm ( mein bhi barabar hon to wo jisne un sab ki nisbat pahley hijrat ki ho, agar wo hijrat mein barabar hon to wo jo Islam qabool karne mein sabqat rakhta (aage) ho. koi insan wahan doosrey insan ki imamat na karey jahan us (doosrey (ka ikhtiyar ho aur uske ghar mein uski qaabil ehtiraam nashist par uski ijazat ke baghair koi na baithey. ( abu-Saeed ( ashajj ne apni riwayat mein Islam qabool karne main ( sabqat (ke bajaey umr main ( sabqat rakhta ho ( hai."
1533,"abu-Muawiya , Jareer, ibne- Fuzel aur Sufiyan sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi manind (tarah) riwayat bayan ki hai."
1534,"Shoba ne Ismail-bin-Rajaa se riwayat ki, kaha : maine aos-bin-zamaj se suna, kehtey they : maine Hazrat abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se kaha : qaum ki imamat wo karey jo Allah ki kitab ko zyada padhney wala aur padhney mein dusron se zyada qadeem (behtar) ho, agar un sab ka padhna aik sa ho to wo imamat karey jo hijrat mein qadeem tar ho, agar hijrat mein sab barabar hon to wo imamat karey jawan sabse umr mein bada ho aur tum kisi shakhs ke ghar aur uske daayra ikhtiyar mein iske imam na bano. na hi iske ghar mein uski qaabil ehtiraam nashist par baitho , haan is sura mein ke wo tumhen (is baat ki) ijazat de ya ( farmaya : ( uski ijazat se."
1535,"Ismail-bin-Ibrahim ( ibne-Ulaih ( ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham se Ayub ne abu-Qilaba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Malik-bin-Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur ham sab naujawaan aur ham umr they, ham ne aap ke paas bees raatein qiyam kya. Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut meharban aur narm dil they, aap ne khayal farmaya ke hamein ghar walon ke paas janey ka ishtiyaaq (shouq) hoga, aap ne ham se hamarey un ghar walon ke barey mein sawal kya jinhein ham chhod aaey they, ham ne aapko bataya to aap ne farmaya : apne ghar walon ke paas lot jao, unhi ke darmyan raho, unhein taleem do aur unhein ( achai par chalney ka ( hukm do, chunanche jab Namaz ka waqt aaey to aik aadmi tum sab ke liye azan kahey , phir tum mein se (jo umr mein) sabse bada ho wo tumhari imamat kare."
1536,Hammad ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki.
1537,"aur yahi hadis hamein ibne-abi-Umar ne sunai, kaha : abdul-wahaab ne bhi Ayub se hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujh se abu-Qilaba ne bayan kya, kaha : hamein abu-Sulaiman-Malik-bin-Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai, kaha : main kuchh logon (ki maiiyat (sath) ( mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir hua, ham taqriban ham umr naujawaan they. . . . . . aagey donon ( Hammad aur abdul-wahaab ( ne ibne-Ulaih ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
1538,"abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne Khalid Haza se, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Malik-bin-Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : main aur mera sathi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, jab ham ne aap ke yahan se waapsii ka irada kya to aap ne ham se farmaya :'' jab Namaz (ka waqt) aaey to azan kaho , phir iqamat kaho aur tum donon mein jo bada ho wo tumhari imamat kar ley.''"
1539,Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Khalid Haza se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur (apni riwayat mein) ye izafa kya ke Haza ne kaha : donon qirat mein aik jaisey they.
1540,"Younus-bin-Yazeed ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat kartey huey khabar di, kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf ne bataya ke un donon ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab namaze-Fajr ki qirat se farigh hotey aur) rukoo mein janey ke liye) takbeer kehtey to sar uthaney ke baad) samii-Allahuliman-Hamiida Rabbana-walakal-hamda ( ) Allah ne sun liya jisne uski hamd ki, aey hamarey rab! aur hamd terey hi liye hai) kehtey, phir haalate-qiyam hi mein aap farmatey : aey Allah ! Waleed-bin-Waleed , Salma-bin-Hisham , ayaash-bin-abi Rabee aur mominon mein se un logon ko jinhein ( kaafiron ne) kamzor paya , nijat ata farmaa. aey Allah ! qabila Muzar par apne raundney ko sakht kar, un par apne us muaakhizey (pakad) ko Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamaney ke qahat ki tarah kar de Allah ! alhayaan, Ri'al, Zakwan aur usaiyyaa par, jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki, laanat nazil kar. phir ham tak ye baat pahunchi ke iske baad jab aap par ye aayat utri : aap ka us mamley se koi sarokaar nahi, ( Allah Taala ( chahey unko tauba ka mauqa ata karey, chahey unko azab de ke wo yaqinan zulm karne waley hain to aap ne ye dua chhod di."
1541,"ibne-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un alfaz tak riwayat ki is sakhti ko un par Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamaney ke qahat ki tarah kar de jo iske baad hai usey bayan nahi kya."
1542,"hamein Auzai ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mahiney tak rukoo ke baad qunoot ( aajizii se dua ( ki, jab aap (samii-Allahuliman-Hamiida) keh letey (to ( apni qunoot mein ye (alfaz ( kehtey : aey Allah ! Waleed bin Waleed ko nijat de, aey Allah ayaash-bin-abi-Rabee ko nijat de, aey Allah kamzor samjhey janey waley (doosrey) mominon ko nijat ata kar, aey Allah ! Muzar par apne raundney ko sakht tar kar aur usey un par, Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke) zamaney ke) qahat ki tarah kar de. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ne ye dua chhod di, maine ( sathiyon se) kaha : main dekhta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dua chhod di hai. kaha : ( jawab mein) mujh se kaha gaya, tum unhein dekhtey nahi, ( jinke liye dua hui thi) wo sab aa chukey hain."
1543,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke (eik roz ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isha ki Namaz padh rahe they, jab aap ne farmaya : ( samii-Allahuliman-Hamiida) to sajdey mein janey se pahley aap ne ( dua maangtey huey) farmaya : aey Allah ayaash-bin-abi Rabee ko nijat ata farmaa. iske baad Yusuf (Alaihissalam) (ke zamaney) ke qahat ki tarah ke alfaz tak Auzai ki riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, baad ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
1544,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Allah ki qism ! zaroor Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ko tum logon ke bahut qareeb karunga, iske baad Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Zuhar, isha aur subah ki Namaz mein qunoot kartey aur musalmanon ke haq mein dua kartey aur kaafiron par laanat bhejtey."
1545,"Ishaq-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un logon ke khilaf jinhoney biarey-maoona walon ko qatl kya tha, tees ( din tak) subah (ki namazon ( mein bad-duaa ki. aap ne Re'al, Zakwaan, Lahyaan aur usaiyya ke khilaf , jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki, bd-dua ki. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ne un logon ke mutaalliq jo biarey-maoona par qatl huey, Quran (ka kuchh hissey ( nazil farmaya jo baad mein mansukh honey tak ham padhtey rahe (is mein shohdaa ka paigham tha) ke hamari qaum ko bata dein ke ham apne rab se ja miley hain, wo ham se razi ho gaya hai aur ham us se razi hain."
1546,"Muhammad (bin-Sirin ( se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (kabhii) subah ki Namaz mein qunoot ki thi? kaha : haan , rukoo se thodi der baad ."
1547,"abu-mujliz ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mahiney tak subah ki Namaz mein rukoo ke baad qunoot ki, aap Re'al aur Zakwan ke khilaf bad-dua farmatey they aur kehtey they : usaiyyaa ne Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki."
1548,"Anas-bin-Sirin ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mahiney tak namaze-Fajr mein rukoo ke baad qunoot ki, aap banu- usaiyyaa ke khilaf bad-dua kartey rahe"
1549,"abu-Muawiya ne Aasim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine un ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) se qunoot ke barey mein puchha : rukoo se pahley hai ya rukoo ke baad ? to unhon-ne kaha : rukoo se pahley. kaha : maine kaha : bahut se log samajhtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo ke baad qunoot ki. to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mahiney qunoot ki, un logon ke khilaf bad-dua farmatey rahe jinhoney aap ke sahaba mein se kuchh logon ko qatl kya tha jinhein qir'a ( Quran padhney waale) kaha jata tha."
1550,"Sufiyan ne Aasim se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey suna, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nahi dekha ke aapko kisi aur jang par itna gham mehsus hua ho jitna un sattar (70) ( sathiyon ( par hua jo bi'arey maoona ke waqiey ke roz Shahid kiye gaey, unhein qir'a kaha (Quraan padhne waaley) jata tha, aap aik mahiney tak unke qaatilon ke khilaf bd-dua kartey rahe."
1551,"Hafs, ibne- Fuzel aur Marwan sab ne Aasim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis riwayat ki, unmein se kuchh ne kuchh se kuchh zyada riwayat kya hai."
1552,"Shoba ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mahiney tak qunoot ki, aap Ra-al, Zakwan aur Usba par laanat bhejtey they jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masiyat ki thi."
1553,Musa bin Anas ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki.
1554,"Hisham ne Qatada ke hawale se Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mahiney tak Arab ke qabaayel mein se kuchh qabeelon ke khilaf baddua kartey huey qunoot ki, phir chhod di."
1555,"Shoba ne Amr-bin-Murra se riwayat ki, kaha : maine ibne-abi-Lela se suna, kaha : hamein Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr aur maghrib (ki namazon ( mein qunoot kya kartey they."
1556,"Sufiyan ne Amr-bin-Murra se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fajr aur maghrib (ki namazon ( mein qunoot ki."
1557,"Imran bin abi Anas ne Hanzala bin Ali se aur unhon-ne Khafaf bin Ema Ghifari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz main ( dua kartey huey) kaha : aey Allah ! banu- Lahyaan : Ra-al, Zakwan aur Usba par laanat bhej jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nafarmani ki. ( ghifaar ( ki Allah maghfirat karey aur Aslam ko Allah salamati ata farmaai ."
1558,"Haaris-bin-Khufaf se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Khufaf-bin-iimaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo kya, phir sar utha kar farmaya : ghifaari ki Allah maghfirat karey, Aslam ko Allah salamati ata kare. aur usaiyyaa ne Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki. aey Allah ! banu- Lahyaan par laanat bhej aur Re'al aur Zakwan par laanat bhej . phir aap sajdey mein chaley gaey. Khufaf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kaafiron par usi ke sabab se laanat ki gaee. (laanat ka tariqa ikhtiyar kya gaya.)"
1559,"(Imran ke bajaey) Abdur-Rehman bin Hurmala ne Hanzala bin Ali-bin Isqaa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Khafaf bin Ema (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, siwaey iske ke unhon-ne kaafiron par usi ke sabab laanat ki gaee ke alfaz nahi kahey ."
1560,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab ke hawale se khabar di, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab jange-khaibar se wapas huey to raat bhar chaltey rahe yahan tak ke jab aapko neend ne aa liya, aap ne ( sawari se) utar kar padao kya aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : hamarey liye raat ka pahra do ( nazar rakho ke Kab subah hoti hai? ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne maqdoor bhar Namaz padhi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba so gaey. jab fajr qareeb hui to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne (matla) fajr ki taraf rukh kartey huey apni sawari ke sath tek lagai, jab wo tek lagaey huey they, to un par neend ghalib aa gaee, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey na Bilal aur na hi unke sahaba mein se koi bedaar hua yahan tak ke un par dhoop padney lagi , sabse pahley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey aur ghabraa gaey. farmaney lagey : aey Bilal! to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : meri jaan ko bhi usi ne qabzey mein ley liya tha jis ne, mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan aey Allah ke rasool! - - - aap ki jaan ko qabzey mein ley liya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sawaariyaan aagey badhaao. wo apni sawaariyon ko lekar kuchh aagey badhey , phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya, unhon-ne Namaz ki iqamat kahi , phir aap ne unko subah ki Namaz padhai , jab Namaz khatm ki to farmaya : jo shakhs Namaz ( padhna ( bhool jaey to jab usey yad aaey usey padhey , Allah Taala ne farmaya : meri yad ke waqt Namaz qaaim karo. Yunus ne kaha : ibne-Shahab se ( للذکرٰی ( ) yad karne ke liye) padhtey they"
1561,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aik shab ham aakhir raat main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath utrey aur na jaagey yahan tak ke suraj nikal aaya tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har shakhs oont ki nakel pakdey ke ye makan hai shaitan kaa. phir ham ne aisa hi kya (yani us maidan se bahar ho gaey ( . phir pani mangaya aur wuzu kya aur 2 rakaat Namaz padhi aur Yaqoob ne sajde ki bajaey 'Salla' kaha phir Namaz ki takbeer hui aur subah ki farz Namaz ada ki.
1562,"Sabit ne Abdullah-bin Ribah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Khattab farmaya aur kaha : tum apni ( poori ( Sham (Syria) aur) poori (raat chaltey rahogey to insha-Allah kal tak pani par pahunch jaogey . log chal padey , koi mud kar doosrey ki taraf dekhta bhi na tha. abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : usi aalim main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaltey rahe yahan tak ke raat aadhi guzar gaee, mein aap ke pahlu mein chal raha tha, kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko oongh aa gaee aur aap sawari se aik taraf jhuk gaey, mein aap ke paas aaya aur aapko jagaaey baghair aapko sahara diya yahan tak ke aap apni sawari par seedhey ho gaey, phir aap chaltey rahe yahan tak ke raat ka beshtar hissey guzar gaya, aap ( phir ( sawari par (eik taraf ( jhukey , kaha : maine aapko jagaaey baghair aapko sahara diya yahan tak ke aap apni sawari par seedhey ho gaey, kaha : phir chaltey rahe yahan tak ke sehrii ka aakhiri waqt tha to aap ( phir ( jhukey , ye jhuknaa pahley donon baar ke jhukney se zyada tha, qareeb tha ke aap oont se gir padtey , main aap ke paas aaya aur aapko sahara diya to aap ne apna sar Mubarak uthaya aur farmaya : ye kon hai? maine kaha : abu Qatada hun. farmaya : tum Kab se mere sath is tarah chal rahe ho? maine kaha : main raat hi se is tarah safar kar raha hun. farmaya : Allah isi tarah tumhari hifazat karey jis tar padhi. tum ne iske Nabi ki hifazat ki. phir farmaya : kya tum dekh rahe ho (ke ( ham logon se ojhal hain? phir puchha : tumhen koi (aur ( nazar aar ہا hai? maine kaha : ye aik sawar hai. phir kaha : ye aik aur sawar hai yahan tak ke ham ikatthey huey to saat (7) sawar they, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rastey se aik taraf hatey , phir sar ( nichey ( rakh diya (aur let gaey ( phir farmaya : hamarey liye hamari Namaz ka khayal rakhna. phir jo sabse pahley jaagey wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi they, suraj aap ki pusht par) chamak raha ( tha, kaha : ham sakht tashwish ke aalim mein khadey huey, phir aap ne farmaya : Sawar ho jao . ham sawar huey aur) aagey ( chal padey yahan tak ke jab suraj buland ho gaya to aap utrey , phir aap ne wuzu ka bartan maanga jo mere sath tha, usi mein kuchh pani tha, kaha : phir aap ne us se ( mukammal ( wuzu ke muqaabley mein kuchh halka wuzu kya, aur is mein kuchh pani bach bhi gaya, phir aap ne (mujhey ( abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : hamarey liye apne wuzu ka bartan mehfooz rakhna , uski aik khabar hogi. phir Bilal ر (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz ke liye azan kahi , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakatein padhein , phir aap ne isi tarah jis tarah roz kartey they subah ki Namaz padhai , kaha : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sawar ho gaey ham bhi aap ke sath Sawar ho gaey, kaha : ham mein se kuchh log aik doosrey se khusur phir karne lagey ke ham ne Namaz mein jo kotahi ki hai iska kaffara kya hai? is par aap ne farmaya : kya tumharey liye mere amal mein namoona nahi ? phir aap ne farmaya : samajh lo ! neend ( aa jana ( main ( kisi ki) koi kotahi nahi. kotahi uski hai jisne ( jaagney ke baad) dusri Namaz ka waqt aa jana tak Namaz nahi padhi, jo is tarah ( neend ( karey to jab uske liye jaagey to ye Namaz padh ley , phir jab doosra din aaey to usey waqt par ada kare. phir farmaya : tum kya dekhtey ho (doosrey ( logon ne kya kya? kaha : phir aap ne farmaya : logon ne subah ki to apne Nabi ko gum paya Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumharey peechhey hain, wo aisey nahi ke tumhen peechhey chhod dein. (doosrey ( logon ne kaha : be-shak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tum se aagey hain. agar wo Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki ا taa'at karein to sahi rastey par chalein gey . kaha : to ham logon tak (is waqt) pahunch paaey jab din chadh aaya tha aur har cheez tap gaee thi aur wo keh rahe they : aey Allah ke rasool! ham piyaa se mar gaey. to aap ne farmaya : tum par koi halaakat nahi aai. phir farmaya : mera chhota piyala mere paas aaney do. kaha : phir wuzu ke pani wala bartan mangwaya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (is se pyaley mein) undeltey gaey aur abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko pilaatey gaey, Ziyad der na guzri thi ke logon ne wuzu ke bartan mein jo ( thoda sa pani ( tha, dekh liya, is par jhurmut bana kar ikatthey hogey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : achchha tariqa ikhtiyar karo, tum mein se har aik achi tarah piyaas bujhaa lega . kaha : logon ne aisa hi kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pani ( pyaley mein) undeltey gaey aur main logon ko pilaataa gaya yahan tak ke mere aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke siwa aur koi na bacha , kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir pani daala aur mujh se farmaya : piyo . maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! jab tak aap nahi pi lengey mein nahi piyun ga . farmaya : qaum ko pani pilaaney wala un sabse aakhir mein peetaa hai. kaha : tab maine pi liya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi nosh farmaya, kaha : iske baad log us haalat main ( agley (pani par pahunchey ke sab ( ne apne ( bartan pani se bharey huey they aur) khub ( sairaab they. ( Sabit ne) kaha, Abdullah-bin Ribah ne kaha : main ye hadis jaame masjid mein sab logon ko sunaunga . tab Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aey jawan ! khayal rakhna ke tum kis tarah hadis bayan kartey ho, us raat mein bhi qafley ke sawaaron mein se aik tha. kaha : maine kaha : aap us hadis ko zyada jaanney waley hain. to unhon-ne puchha : tum kis qabeeley se ho? maine kaha Ansar se. farmaya : hadis bayan karo tum apni hadison se zyada aagah ho ( Ansar mein se abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne us sarey waqiey ka sabse zyada aur baareekii se mushaahida kya tha balke wo us sarey waqiey main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saath-saath they, aagey unse sunney waley Abdullah-bin Ribah bhi Ansar mein se they. ( kaha : maine logon ko hadis sunai to Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is raat mein main bhi maujood tha aur main nahi samajhta ke usey kisi ne is tarah ya dar kha jis tarah tum ne usey ya rakha hai."
1563,"Salam bin Zareer Utaridi ne kaha : maine abu -Rijaa Utaridi se suna, wo Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kar rahe they, kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik safar mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha, ham us raat chaltey rahe yahan tak ke jab subah qareeb aai to ham ( thakaawat ke sabab ( utar padey , ham par) neend mein doobi) aankhen ghalib aa gain yahan tak ke suraj chamakney laga. ham mein jo sabse pahley bedaar huey wo Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so jatey to ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jagaaya nahi kartey they yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud bedaar ho jatey, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) jaagey , wo Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb khadey ho gaey aur) Allahu-akbar ( pukarney lagey aur (is ( takbeer mein awaz unchi karne lagey yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi jaag gaey, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar uthaya aur dekha ke suraj chamak raha hai to farmaya : ( aagey ( chalo. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein lekar chaley yahan tak ke suraj (roshan) ho kar safaid ho gaya, aap utarey, hamein subah ki Namaz padhai. logon mein se aik aadmi alag ho gaya aur us ne hamarey sath Namaz na padhi, jab salam phera to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se kaha : falan ! tum ne hamarey sath Namaz kyon nahi padhi ? usne kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! mujhey janabat laahiq ho gaee (yaani raat maine apni bivi se hambistari ki) hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey hukm diya. us ne mitti se tayammum kya aur Namaz padhi, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey chand sawaaron samet pani ki talash mein jaldi apne aagey rawaana kya, ham sakht piyaasey they, jab ham chal rahe they, to hamein aik aurat mili jisne apne paon 2 mashkon ke darmyan latka rakhey they ( badi mashkon samet paon latkaey , oont par Sawar thi) , ham ne us se puchha : pani kahan hai? kehney lagi : afsos ! tumharey liye pani nahi hai. ham ne puchha : tumharey ghar aur pani ke darmyan kitna fasla hai? usne kaha : aik din aur raat ki masafat hai. ham ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas chalo. kehney lagi : Allah ka rasool kya hota hai? ham ne usey uske mamley main ( faisley ka ( kuchh ikhtiyar na diya yahan tak ke usey ley aaey iske sath ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney hazir huey, aap ne us se puchha to usne aapko isi tarah bataya jis tarah hamein bataya tha, aur aapko ye bhi bataya ke wo yateem bachchon wali hai, iske ( zer kifaalat ( bahut se yateem bachchey hain. aap ne uski pani dhoney wali ontni ke barey mein hukm diya, usey bitha diya gaya aur aap ne kulli karke mushkon ke uper ke donon suraakhon mein pani daala, phir aap ne uski ontni ko khada kya to ham sab ne aur ham chalis (40) (shadeed ( piyaasey afraad they (un mushkon se) pani piyaa yahan tak ke ham sairaab ho gaey aur hamarey paas jitni mashkein aur pani ke bartan they sab bhar liye aur apne sathi ko ghusl bhi karaya , albatta ham ne kisi oont ko pani na pilaya aur wo yani donon mashkein pani (ki miqdar zyada ho janey ke sabab ( phatney wali ho gain , phir aap ne farmaya : tumharey paas jo kuchh hai, ley aao . ham ne tukdey aur khajoorein ikatthi kin, uske liye aik thaili ka munh band kar diya gaya to aap ne us se kaha : jao aur ye khuraak apne bachchon ko khilaao aur jaan lo ! ham ne tumharey pani mein kami nahi ki. jab wo apne ghar walon ke paas pahunchi to kaha : main insanon ke sabse badey saahir se mil kar aai hon ya phir jis tarah ke wo khud ko samajhta hai, wo Nabi hai, aur iska mamla is-is tarah se hai. phir ( aakhir kaar ( Allah ne us aurat ke sabab se logon se kati hui us aabadi ko hidayat ata kar di, wo musalman ho gaee aur) baqi ( log bhi musalman ho gaey. (ye pichhley waqiey se milta jaltaa aik aur waqia hai.)"
1564,"Auf-bin-abi jameela dehati ne abu -Rijaa Utaridi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham aik safar ke doran main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, ham aik raat chaley, jab raat ka aakhiri hissey aaya, subah se thodi der pahley ham is tarah pad kar so gaey ke us se zyada meethi neend aik musaafir ke liye aur koi nahi ho sakti , hamein suraj ki haraarat hi ne jagaaya . . . . phir Salam bin Zareer ki hadis ki tarah hadis sunai aur kuchh kami beshi bhi ki aur (apni riwayat ki hui ( hadis mein unhon-ne kaha : jab umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) jaagey aur logon ki sura haal dekhi , aur wo buland awaz aadmi they, to unhon-ne unchi awaz se ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke oonchey ( Allahu-akbar ( kehney se jaag gaey, jab Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jaag gaey to logon ne apne us mamley ki shikayat ki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi ( bada ( nuqsan nahi hua, ( aagey ( chalo. . . . . . . aagey wahi hadis bayan ki."
1565,"Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab safar mein hotey aur raat (ke aakhiri hissey ( mein aaraam ke liye let'tey to daain pahlu par let'tey aur jab subah se zara pahley let'tey to apni kohni khadi kar letey aur sar hatheli par takaa letey. (taake zyada gehri neend na aaey. us hadis ke alfaz bhi is baat ki taaid kartey hain ke uper bayan kiye gaey 2 alag alag waqiey hain. ("
1566,"Hammam ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Qatada ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs koi Namaz bhool jaey to jaisey hi wo usey yad aaey, wo Namaz padh ley , us Namaz ka iske ilawa aur koi kaffara nahi. Qatada ne padha : aur meri yad ke waqt Namaz qaaim karein."
1567,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( yahi hadis) riwayat ki, albatta unhon-ne iske ilawa iska aur koi kaffara nahi ke alfaz riwayat nahi kiye."
1568,"Saeed ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, kaha : Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs koi Namaz bhool gaya ya usey ada kartey waqt sota reh gaya to us (namaz (ka kaffara yahi hai ke jab usey yad aaey wo us Namaz ko padh ley."
1569,"Musanna ne Qatada ke hawale se Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi Namaz ( padhney ke waqt us ( se soyaa rahe ya us se ghaafil ho jaey to jab usey yad aaey wo (namaz ( padh ley , be-shak Allah Taala ne ( khud ( irshad farmaya hai : aur meri yad ke waqt Namaz qaaim karo."
